Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) cyakwirakwiriye mu buryo bwihuse mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Kuba icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) cyongeye kwiyongera mu bihugu bigize EU/European Economic Area n'u Bwongereza, bigaragaza ko nubwo icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyagiye kigaragara mu bihugu bitandukanye, ariko kigenda gikwirakwira mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ubunararibonye bw'uburwayi bw'Ubutaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bigomba kurushaho kwitegura guhangana n'igihombo kinini cy'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye ubuvuzi bw'abaganga, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bw'indembe.
Ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2020, hari itsinda ry'abarwayi ba Pneumonia bataramenyekana icyateye muri Wuhan, mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara cyatangaje ko iki cyorezo cyatewe n'ubwoko bushya bwa coronavirus, ubu buzwi ku izina rya SARS-CoV-2.
Kuva icyo gihe, uburwayi buterwa no kwandura SARS-CoV-2 bwiswe indwara ya coronavirus (COVID-19).
Ibikoresho biriho kugeza ubu byerekana ko hafi 80% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwara indwara yoroheje y'ubuhumekero, hamwe cyangwa badafite uburwayi bw'ibihaha, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 yabaye indwara ikomeye cyane, bituma abarwayi bajya mu bitaro, mu gihe abasigaye 6% bari barwaye cyane, bajya mu bitaro byita ku barwayi bababaye cyane.
Umubare w'abarwayi bapfa bavuye muri Covid-19 mu bitaro ni 4% gusa.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, twasuzumye uko ubwandu bwa COVID-19 bwagiye bufata indi ntera muri buri gihugu cyo mu Muryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, tugereranya n'uko byagenze mu Ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Twakomeje tugereranya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza
Nyuma y'aho COVID-19 ikwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa, ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu bindi bice by'isi ryakurikiyeho.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) yatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu kinyamakuru Eurosurveillance cyo ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe 2020, Spiteri na bagenzi be batangaje ko ari we muntu wa mbere w'Umunyamerika wanduye coronavirus nk'uko byasobanuwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima.
Mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'uburayi/akarere k'ubukungu bw'uburayi, abarwayi ba mbere bemejwe batangajwe n'Ubufaransa ku ya 24 Mutarama 2020 mu bagenzi bagarutse baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020, abantu bose 30 bo mu Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza (UK) bari baranduye COVID-19, kandi kuva ku ya 31 Ukuboza 2019 kugeza ku iherezo ry'uko kwezi, abantu 39,768 banduye na 1,727 bapfuye, mu gihe mu Butaliyani honyine hari abantu 1,7750, n'abantu 1,441 bapfuye.
Gufata imibare y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 hamwe n'ibimenyetso by'abarwayi
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara (ECDC), gitanga amakuru y'ibimenyetso by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 byemejwe mu bihugu byose by'isi buri munsi, biturutse ku makuru yatanzwe n'inzego z'ibanze, nk'abakozi ba Minisiteri y'Ubuzima, inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu n'iz'akarere, n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Aya makuru yakoreshejwe mu gusuzuma uko COVID-19 iteye mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, no kubigereranya n'u Butaliyani.
Mu rwego rwo kumenya umubare w'abantu banduye COVID-19, twabaze igihe cy'iminsi 14 cy'ubwandu bw'abarwayi ba COVID-19, bityo igihe gisanzwe cya COVID-19 muri buri gihugu cy'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, mu gihe kuva ku ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Umubare w'abarwayi muri buri gihugu ugereranyijwe n'umubare w'abarwayi bose mu gihe cy'itariki ya 08:00 za mu gitondo cyo ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020 ugereranyije n'umubare w'abarwayi bose mu gihe cy'itariki ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Imibare y'ubwandu bwa COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza
Imyiteguro y'ibyabaye mu minsi 14 y'ibura ry'ibyago bya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi no mu Bwongereza, muri rusange yari ihuje n'ibyabaye mu Ntara ya Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Igishushanyo cya 1).
Muri rusange, mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangiye ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, hanyuma kigenda kizamuka ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020.
Ibi ahanini byatewe n'ubwiyongere bwihuse bw'ibyago by'indwara byatangajwe mu Butaliyani, ariko ibindi bihugu byose bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza na byo byerekana ko byiyongereye ku mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 (igishakishwa mu mwandiko wunganira).
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza ingano y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'u Bwongereza, ugereranyije n'abanduye mu Butaliyani kuva ku ya 31 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ryasobanuye ko kugeza saa munani za mu gitondo z'itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibindi bihugu 15 bigize EU/European Economic Area n'Ubwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye, ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bitatu bishize cyangwa munsi yayo.
Ibisubizo byacu byerekana ko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza wiyongera cyane.
Imyiteguro igaragara mu kwiyongera kwa COVID-19 igaragaza ko icyorezo cyakwirakwira mu bihugu byose ku muvuduko umwe.
Nubwo ibihugu bitandukanye biri mu byiciro bitandukanye by'icyorezo, hari itandukaniro mu buryo inzego z'ubuzima z'ibihugu zitabira, kandi ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibipimo bitandukanye ku bantu bagomba gupimwa cyangwa gupimwa COVID-19.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu duce twanduye mu Butaliyani batangaje ko abagera kuri 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, kandi amakuru aturuka mu bitangazamakuru avuga ko ubushobozi bwose bw'ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe byamaze kuzura.
Kugeza ubu, mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA, amakuru y'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakirwa mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu bigo by'indembe ari mu bihugu 6% na 1% gusa (nta makuru agaragara).
Ariko kandi, bigomba gukusanywa mu buryo bufite gahunda kugira ngo bikoreshwe nk'inyongera ku makuru y'ubugenzuzi, kandi bibanze ku bice bimwe na bimwe byatangajwe n'ibice by'urupfu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje itandukaniro rinini mu kubona ibitanda by'indembe n'ibisanzwe mu Burayi, aho ibitanda biri hagati ya 29.2 mu Budage na 4.2 muri Portugal ku baturage 100,000.
Ibi bivuze ko ibyo bihugu bifite ibikoresho byinshi cyangwa bike ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (uburiri 12,5 bwo kwita ku barwayi bakomeye ku baturage 100,000 mu 11-2010).
Ibipimo by'imikorere bijyanye n'ubwiyongere bw'ubushobozi bwo kuvura hamwe n'ibyerekezo kuri buri gihugu cy'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza ku bijyanye n'umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 barwariye mu bitaro bafite ibyago > 90% byo kurenga ubushobozi bw'ibitanda byo mu bitaro bya ICU byatanzwe mu buryo bw'igenzura ry'ingamba rya gatandatu rya ECDC ku bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko abantu banduye bagaragaye mu matsinda mu bice bimwe na bimwe by'ibihugu bigize EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, kandi ibitaro n'ibitaro byita ku barwayi bafite uburwayi budasanzwe bikorera abaturage bo mu karere kamwe, amakuru yerekeye abantu banduye n'ibitanda byita ku barwayi bafite uburwayi budasanzwe agomba gutangazwa mbere na mbere hakurikijwe uburyo bw'ibice by'akarere ku rwego rwa 2 rw'ibarurishamibare (NUTS-2).
Uburyo iki cyorezo cyatangiye mu Butaliyani n'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiri kwiyongera mu bihugu bigize EU/EEA n'u Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibyumba by'indembe bigomba kwitegura guhangana n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 kandi bigashyiraho uburyo bwo kwakira abarwayi ba COVID-19, cyane cyane mu byumba by'indembe, nk'uko byagenze mu turere twanduye two mu Butaliyani.
Nk'uko byagaragajwe mu igenzura ryihuse ry'ibyago bya ECDC, uburyo bwihuse, budahangarwa kandi bwuzuye ni ngombwa mu kugabanya ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2 hamwe no guhindura imyumvire kuva ku kugabanya ingamba ku kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo, kuko niba ingamba zikenewe zitarakozwe hakiri kare, kwiyongera vuba kw'umubare w'abarwayi bishobora kutaha abayobozi n'ibitaro umwanya uhagije wo gutahura, kwakira no gushyira mu bikorwa ibisubizo bikwiye.
Isesengura ryihuse ry'ibyago kandi rigaragaza ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo.
Ibihugu bifite umwanya muto wo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya no kugabanya umuvuduko wo gukwirakwira kwa SARS-CoV-2, bityo bikagabanya igitutu ku mashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi.
Iyo ibyo bitabaye, mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru biri imbere, inzego z'ubuzima mu bindi bihugu by'Umuryango w'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'Ubukungu bw'u Burayi zishobora guhura n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), giterwa na SARS-CoV-2, kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000, ndetse n'abarenga 80,000 barwara iki cyorezo mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, bituma kiza ku isonga mu byago by'ubumuntu.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kuba yandura binyuze mu ducurama, nk'uko byagenze kuri SARS-CoV yatumye abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi bagerwaho na SARS mu 2003.
Nubwo COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubukana buke ugereranyije na SARS, ariko yandura cyane kandi ikandura abantu bakuze n'abagabo kurusha abakiri bato n'abagore.
Mu gusubiza umubare w'ibitabo byandikirwa kuri iyi ndwara iri kuvuka, iki kigo kigerageza gutanga isesengura ryuzuye kandi ryuzuye ry'iki kibazo cy'ubushakashatsi.
Tuzatanga amakuru y'ibanze ajyanye n'icyorezo, etiology, virology, gusuzuma, kuvura, kwirinda no kwirinda indwara.
Nubwo ibibazo byinshi bikiri bitarashubijwe, iki cyifuzo cy'ubushakashatsi ni uko cyafasha mu kumenya iyi ndwara y'uburwayi kandi ikayirandura.
Umunsi mukuru w'impeshyi wabaye tariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye ikintu kitazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose basabwe kuguma mu rugo mu gihe cyose cy'ikiruhuko ndetse n'ibyumweru byinshi nyuma yaho kubera icyorezo gishya cya virusi.
Iyi virusi ifite ubukana bwinshi na koronavirusi (CoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cya SARS mu 2003; ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, OMS yahisemo kuyita SARS-CoV-2 n'izina ry'indwara ifitanye isano na yo, CoV Disease-19 (COVID-19) (indwara ya koronavirusi-19 cyangwa COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cyatangiriye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, maze gikwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri bitanu ku isi.
Kuva ku ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi imaze guhitana abantu barenga 80.000, umubare w'abarwayi barekuwe urenga 40.000, n'abantu barenga 3.000 bapfuye.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere ku isi" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nk'uko bigaragara mu makuru ya PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/), mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, inyandiko zisaga 200 z'ubushakashatsi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 zagiye zisohoka, zirimo izijyanye n'ubumenyi bw'ubwandu bw'indwara, indwara z'ibyorezo, etiology, gusuzuma no kuvura, kuva ubwo hatangajwe inyandiko ya mbere ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020 yerekana uko virusi yakurikiranye mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga, yakuwe mu bipimo by'abarwayi benshi.
Iki cyigisho cy'isesengura kigamije gusubiramo iterambere ry'ubushakashatsi mu bice bishya kandi by'ingenzi.
Mu bice bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara iterwa na coronavirus yitwa Middle East Respiratory Syndrome (MERS) yatangiye kugaragara mu 2012.
Turareba ibyo twize kugeza ubu ku bijyanye no kwirinda no kwanduza indwara, ariko nanone tugiye gusuzuma ibibazo bimwe na bimwe by'ingenzi.
Coronavirus zisanzwe zisanzwe ari indwara zidakora ku bantu, zitera 15% by'ibicurane bisanzwe.
Ariko kandi, muri iki kinyejana, twahuye inshuro ebyiri na SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye haba icyorezo cya mbere mu 2003 mu Bushinwa na 2012 muri Arabiya Sawudite, kandi nyuma y'igihe gito zikwirakwira mu bindi bihugu zituma abantu benshi barwara kandi bagapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni yo ndwara ya gatatu ya coronavirus imaze kwaduka mu mateka y'abantu.
Nk'uko bigaragara ku ishusho ya 1, uduhimba tw'indwara z'ibicurane tudafite inkomoko zitazwi twatangajwe bwa mbere ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 tuvuye i Wuhan muri Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, virusi ya Corona yatangiye gukwirakwira.
Ku ya 15 Mutarama 2020, umuntu wa mbere wanduye iki cyorezo yatangajwe avuye mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Hagati aho, icyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu mijyi ituje, mu zindi ntara no mu bihugu bitandukanye.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, abakozi b'ubuzima na serivisi z'ubuvuzi batangajwe ko banduye, byerekana ko virusi ishobora kwanduzwa n'abantu.
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warangije gufunga abantu, kandi abantu bose bari bahatembereye barahagaritswe.
Ku ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku barwayi b'iyi ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 40 b'ukuri, 21 gusa ari bo bahuye mu buryo butaziguye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho icyorezo cyatangiriye giturutse ku nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku ya 30 Mutarama, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ingorabahizi ku isi.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yatangazwaga, iki cyorezo cyamaze kugera mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi.
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka mu buryo bwihuse, hagomba gushyirwaho urugero n'uburemere bw'icyorezo.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ibigo byinshi ku barwayi 8,866 ba coronavirus barimo 4,021 bafite COVID-19 bagaragaje ko iki cyorezo ari icy'igihe gito (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UlBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
