Ubusanzwe, umuriro ni cyo kimenyetso cya mbere cya COVID-19, gishobora kwigaragaza cyonyine cyangwa se kikaba kijyana n'ibindi bimenyetso nk'umuhogo utose, guhumeka nabi, ububabare bw'imisatsi, isesemi, umutwe, ububabare bwo mu muhogo, gutakaza amazi, ububabare bwo mu gatuza, iseseme, kugira iseseme no gucibwamwo.
Bamwe mu barwayi bagaragaje guhumeka nabi no/cyangwa kugabanya umwuka wa ogisijeni mu mubiri nyuma y'icyumweru kimwe batangiye kurwara.
Mu barwayi barwaye indwara zikomeye z'umugongo, ibimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero, guhungabana mu mubiri, acidosis ya metabolic n'ihungabana ry'amaraso byagaragaraga mu barwayi.
Abarwayi bafite umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero n'umuriro ukabije, nubwo nta bidasanzwe biboneka mu mashusho y'ibihaha, bagomba gukorerwa isuzuma kugira ngo bamenye vuba ko banduye virusi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mpera z'Ukuboza 2019 bwagaragaje ko 98% by'abarwayi bagaragaje ibimenyetso nk'ibi bikurikira: umuriro, 76% bari bafite inkorora yumye, 55% bari bafite ikibazo cyo guhumeka, 3% bari bafite iseseme; 8% bari bakeneye gufashwa guhumeka.
Ibisubizo nk'ibyo byatangajwe mu bushakashatsi bubiri buherutse gukorwa, bwagaragaje ko hari itsinda ry'abantu bafite ibimenyetso by'ubwandu, n'irindi ry'abantu batagira ibimenyetso.
Mu kugereranya, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu mwaka wa 2012 bwagaragaje ko abarwayi ba MERS-CoV bafite umuriro (98%), inkorora yumye (47%) n'agahinda ko guhumeka (55%) nk'ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'indwara.
Ariko, 80% muri bo bari bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka, bari benshi cyane kurusha abarwayi ba COVID-19 kandi bihuye n'umubare munini w'abapfa muri MERS ugereranyije na COVID-19.
Kuribwa iseseme (26%), no kubabara mu muhogo (21%), na byo byagaragaraga mu barwayi ba MERS.
Mu barwayi ba SARS, ibimenyetso by'ingenzi byaranze iyi ndwara harimo umuriro (99%-100%), inkorora yumye (29%-75%), guhumeka nabi (40%-42%), iseseme (20%-25%) n'ububabare bw'umugongo (13%-25%), kandi abagera kuri 14%-20% bari bakeneye ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Kugeza ku ya 14 Gashyantare, ubwo imibare y'abamaze kwandura COVID-19 ku isi yose yageraga ku 66,576, umubare w'abamaze gupfa ku isi yose wavuye kuri 2%.
Mu kugereranya, igipimo cy'urupfu rwa SARS kugeza mu Gushyingo 2002 cyari 10% ku barwayi 8,096 bari bamaze kwemezwa.
Ku bijyanye na MERS, imibare y'abapfa ku barwayi 2,494 ni 37%, nk'uko byemejwe n'ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Kamena 2012.
