Ku bw'ibyo, kugenzura icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 ni ikibazo gikomeye cyane kurusha MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV.
Amatsinda akunze gutangirira mu muryango cyangwa mu muryango cyangwa mu modoka imwe nk'ubwato bw'imyidagaduro.
Abarwayi bakunze kuba barigeze gutembera cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyangwa ahandi hantu habonetse ubwandu cyangwa bakaba barigeze guhura n'abantu banduye cyangwa abarwayi mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mbere y'uko icyorezo gitangira.
Icyakora, hari amakuru avuga ko abantu bashobora kwandura virusi mu gihe kirenze ibyumweru bibiri nta bimenyetso bagaragaza, kandi ko abarwayi bakize bavuye mu bitaro bashobora kuba bagifite virusi, ibyo bikaba byaratumye hatangwa umuburo wo kongera igihe cyo gushyirwa mu kato.
Mu cyiciro cya mbere, umubare w'utugingo tw'umweru (cyane cyane utw'imyakura) mu barwayi uba usanzwe cyangwa ugabanutse.
Urugero, impyiko z'amaraso zifite umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso twera uri munsi ya 10×9×4 kuri litiro, harimo umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso turi munsi ya 10×1 kuri litiro, hamwe n'umubare w'aspartate yanduye cyane mu maraso (virusi mu maraso) byabonetse mu barwayi 1,099 ba COVID-19.
Ibipimo bya enzymes z'umwijima n'umusatsi na myoglobin mu maraso byazamutse cyane mu barwayi bamwe, kandi poroteyine C ikora hamwe n'imyanya y'amaraso yo mu maraso y'indwara nyinshi byazamutse.
Mu bantu barwaye cyane, D-dimer, ikorwa n'amaraso yo gusenya fibrin, yariyongereye, umubare w'utugingo tw'amaraso ugabanuka.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe mu mashusho ya radiyo y'igituza bigaragara ku barwayi benshi ba COVID-19 kandi birimo ibicucu cyangwa ibibyimba byo mu bihaha.
Abarwayi bakunze kugira uburwayi bw'ibihaha budasanzwe, kwangirika kw'ibihaha bikaze n'indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba (ARDS).
Iyo indwara y'ubuhumekero buteye ubwoba ibayeho, ubuhumekero ntibucungurwa, amazi menshi n'imyanya ndangagitsina y'imbere mu mubiri bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku guhanahana umwuka.
Imikorere mibi ya nimocytes z'ibihaha by'ubwoko bumwe n'ubw'ubwoko bubiri igabanya ingano ya surfactant, bigatuma ubukana bw'urusobe bw'ibihaha bwiyongera, ibyo bikaba bigabanya ubushobozi bw'ibihaha bwo kwaguka kandi bigatuma ibyago byo gufunga ibihaha byiyongera.
Bityo rero, ibipimo bibi cyane bya radiographie y'igituza byari bihuye n'ibipimo bikomeye by'indwara.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, isesengura rya mbere ry'indwara ya COVID-19 ryatangaje ibimenyetso bikurikira: kubura imyanya y'ubuhumekero, guhuma kw'ibice by'ibihaha, kwangiza udutsi tw'indwara z'ibihaha no kubona ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibihaha mu bihaha by'abarwayi bapfuye kubera iyo ndwara; ibimenyetso bihuye n'indwara y'ubwandu bwa virusi na ARDS (Acute Respiratory Dystress Syndrome) kandi bisa n'ibimenyetso by'abarwayi ba SARS na MERS.
Kumenya RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 hakoreshejwe RT-PCR (Reverse Polymerase Transcriptase Chain Reaction) nk'ikigo cy'ibanze cyo kumenya COVID-19.
Ariko kubera ko igipimo cy'ibinyoma byinshi bishobora gutuma iki cyorezo kigabanuka, kuva ku ya 13 Gashyantare 2020, mu Bushinwa hatangiye gukoreshwa uburyo bwo gupima indwara (uburyo bwo gupima butakibanda ku buryo bwa RT-PCR gusa).
Ibintu nk'ibyo byabaye no mu gihe cyo gusuzuma SARS.
Ku bw'ibyo, guhuza amateka y'uburwayi, ibimenyetso by'uburwayi, ibizamini byo muri laboratwari n'ibisubizo bya radiyoloji ni ngombwa kugira ngo haboneke umuti.
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare 2020, itsinda rya Feng Zhang ryatangaje uburyo bwo gupima virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 hakoreshejwe CRISPR, ubwo ibice bya RNA by'ikoranabuhanga bya SARS-CoV-2 mu bunini bwa <18-</sup>10 × 20 moles kuri litiro kugeza <18-</sup>10 × 200 moles kuri litiro (amakopi 100-10 kuri microliter yinjira) byemezwa n'inkoni mu gihe kitarenze isaha, bidakeneye ibikoresho bikomeye.
Byitezwe ko ubu buryo bushya bushobora kuzamura ububabare n'ubwiyumvo mu gihe bwemejwe mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi.
Kubera kubura ubunararibonye mu kuvura coronavirus nshya, abaganga bakomeje kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 mu buryo bw'ubufasha, ariko bagerageza gukoresha uburyo butandukanye bwo kuvura bwakoreshejwe cyangwa bwatanzwe mu kuvura indwara za mbere za coronavirus zirimo SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na virusi (Imbonerahamwe ya 2).
Muri izo miti harimo imiti yo mu mutwe, imiti ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura virusi, imiti igabanya ubwirinzi bw'umubiri, siteroyi, plasma y'abarwayi bakize, imiti y'Abashinwa n'ubufasha bwo mu mutwe.
Ndetse hatanzwe igitekerezo cyo gukoresha plasma y'abarwayi bakize mu kuvura abarwayi bashya.
Amashyirahamwe y'ubuvuzi arimo guhatana mu gukora imiti n'inkingo za virusi.
SARS-CoV-2 mu mizo ya mbere yibasira cyane ibihaha, kandi bishoboka ko mu rugero ruciriritse, ibindi bice byerekana ACE2 receptor, nk'urwungano rw'amaraso n'impyiko.
Icyakora, guhumeka nabi n'uburwayi bwo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero ni byo bibangamiye abarwayi cyane kandi ni byo bituma benshi bapfa.
Ku bw'ibyo, uburyo bwo guhumeka bufasha ni ingenzi cyane mu kugabanya ibimenyetso no kurokora ubuzima bw'abarwayi, bukaba bukubiyemo imiti isanzwe ya ogisijeni, ikwirakwira ry'umwuka wa ogisijeni, umwuka uhumeka utari uw'ubwandu n'umuvuduko w'ubuhumekero bw'ubwonko bitewe n'uburemere bw'indwara.
Abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka bagomba guhabwa umwuka wa oxygénation exocentricale (ECMO), uburyo bwo kuvura umutima nyuma yo kuvura bwakozwe mbere, bwakoreshejwe mu kuvura umutima udakora neza cyangwa guhumeka nabi.
Byongeye kandi, kubungabunga ubusumbane bwa electrolyte, kwirinda no kuvura ubwandu bw'ibanze n'imiterere y'uburwayi, no kurinda imikorere y'ingingo z'ingenzi ni ingenzi cyane ku barwayi banduye SARS-CoV-2.
Byaragaragaye ko cytoquin ari kimwe mu bintu bituma abarwayi barwaye SARS na MERS bagira ubwirinzi bw'umubiri burenze urugero.
Cytocyanin cystorm ni uburyo bwo kubyimba umubiri, bugaragarira mu kugabanya cytokines nyinshi zirimo TNFα, IL-1β, IL-2, IL-6, IFNα, IFNβ, IFNγ na MCP-1.
Izi cytokines zituma ingirabuzimafatizo z'umubiri zidakora neza zisohora ibinyigishi byinshi by'umudendezo, bikaba ari byo bituma indwara ya ARDS n'izindi ndwara z'ingingo zidakora neza.
Guteza igitutu abarwayi cyane cyane abarwayi barwaye cyane, ni ngombwa mu kuvura cyorezo cya cytokine.
Imiti yitwa corticosteroids na tucylisomab, umuti urwanya IL6 ukoreshwa mu kuvura ibicurane by'imiti yitwa cytokines.
Ubundi buryo bwo kuvura bugabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri bwa cytoquin storm burimo: kugabanya ibisubizo by'ubushobozi bw'umubiri biterwa n'ingirabuzimafatizo za T; kubuza IFN-γ, IL-1 na TNF gukora; kubuza JAK; Blenatumomb; kubuza cytoquin signaling 4; no kubuza HDAC.
Steroids zakoreshejwe cyane mu kuvura SARS nk'imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri mu rwego rwo kugabanya ubukana bw'ibyangiritse.
Icyakora, gukoresha steroid mu rugero rwagutse ntibyatanze umusaruro mu kuvura ibikomere bikomeye by'ibihaha mu barwayi ba COVID-19 na SARS.
Ahubwo, bishobora gutera ibibazo bikomeye, cyane cyane uburwayi bw'amagufwa buterwa no kutagira amaraso menshi, bigira ingaruka zikomeye ku bimenyetso by'indwara.
Icyakora, byasabwe ko hakorwa ubushakashatsi ku miti ya corticosteroids y'ibipimo biri hasi cyangwa biri hagati mu gihe gito, mu rwego rwo kuvura abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafite ibibazo.
Mu gihe iyi nkuru yandikwaga, nta muti wa virusi ushoboye kwemezwa.
Icyakora, gutera umuti witwa Remdesivir mu muhogo, ari analogue ya nucleotide, byagize ingaruka nziza ku murwayi wo muri Amerika warwaye COVID-19.
RedSevier ni umuti mushya wa virusi wakozwe na Gilead mu rwego rwo kuvura indwara ziterwa na virusi ya Ebola na Marburg.
Nyuma yaho, byaje kugaragara ko umuti wa Redsevir ushobora no kubuza virusi zindi zifite RNA imwe, harimo virusi ya MERS na SARS.
Gilead yashyize uru ruganda mu Bushinwa kugira ngo rukore ibizamini bibiri bya muganga ku bantu banduye SARS-CoV-2, kandi byagize ingaruka nziza.
Byongeye kandi, baricetinib, interferon alfa, lupinavir/ritonavir na ribavirin na byo byakoreshejwe nk'imiti ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso bikomeye byo guhumeka.
Kurwara iseseme, kugira iseseme, gusubiranamo, kwangirika kw'impyiko n'ibindi bintu bishobora kubaho nyuma yo gufatwa n'umuti wa lupinavir/ritonavir.
Ibiganiro hagati y'iyi miti n'indi ikoreshwa n'umurwayi bigomba gusuzumwa neza.
Plasma y'abarwayi yarakize kandi haboneka abanduye.
Gukusanya amaraso y'abarwayi bakize indwara yandura, mu rwego rwo kuvura abandi barwayi bafite iyo ndwara cyangwa kurinda abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza indwara yandura, ni ibintu bimaze igihe.
Mu by'ukuri, abarwayi bakize akenshi bagira ibipimo biri hejuru by'abanduye mu maraso yabo.
Antibodies ni immunoglobulins (Ig) zikorwa na B lymphocytes mu kurwanya indwara n'ibindi bintu bituruka hanze, zigaragaza molekile zihariye mu ndwara kandi zikazihagarika mu buryo butaziguye.
Ibi byatumye plasma ikurwa mu itsinda ry'abarwayi bakize COVID-19 maze igahabwa abarwayi 10 bari barwaye cyane.
Ibimenyetso byabo byaragabanutse mu masaha 24, kandi kugabanuka kw'ubuhumekero, kugabanuka kw'umubare w'ubwandu bwa virusi no kuzura neza kwa ogisijeni mu maraso byagaragaraga.
Ariko, gutanga ubu buryo ku buryo bukoreshwa ku kigero kinini bisaba ko bwemezwa kandi bugashyirwa ahagaragara mbere yuko uburyo bwihariye bwo kuvura butangwa.
Byongeye kandi, uretse ingaruka z'ubuvuzi, hari n'ingaruka mbi ziterwa no gukoresha plasma.
Urugero, abanduye bashobora gukabya gutera ibyiyumvo byo kwirinda indwara, bigatuma habaho indwara yo kugabanya imikorere y'imiti yitwa cytokines, ishobora no gutuma umuntu yica.
Ubusanzwe, ibipimo by'abanduye mu maraso biba ari hasi, bityo abantu barwaye cyane bakaba bakeneye plasma nyinshi mu rwego rwo kuvurwa.
Kugira ubushobozi bwo gukora no gukora udukoko tw'ubwoko runaka mu gihe gito cyane cyo guhangana n'icyorezo cy'icyorezo ni ikibazo gikomeye.
Ku bw'ibyo, gutandukanya uturemangingo twa B n'abarwayi bakize no kumenya kode za jenoside zandika za antibody z'ingirakamaro cyangwa gupima za antibody z'ingirakamaro ku maporoteyini ya virusi z'ingirakamaro ni ingenzi kandi birashoboka.
Ibyo bishobora gutuma umuntu ahita akora za rukingo.
Ubuvuzi gakondo bwakoreshejwe mu Bushinwa mu myaka ibihumbi n'ibihumbi mu kuvura indwara zitandukanye.
Ariko kandi, ingaruka zabyo ahanini zishingira ku guhuza ibintu byinshi mu buryo bushingiye ku bushakashatsi bushingiye ku bitekerezo by'ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa.
Ibyinshi mu bikoresho bikora neza ntibiramenyekana cyangwa ntibisobanutse neza kuko kuvanaho no kwemeza ibyo bikoresho cyangwa uburyo bwiza bwo kubishyira hamwe bigoye.
Kugeza ubu, kubera ko nta muti wihariye kandi ufasha COVID-19, TCM (ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa) ni bumwe mu buryo bw'ingenzi bwo kuvura abarwayi bafite ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa byoroheje cyangwa abakize indwara zikomeye.
Urugero, byagaragariye ko imiti ya Shu Feng Jie Du na Lian Hua Qing Wen ikoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19 igira ingaruka nziza.
Ibipimo byo gukira bya COVID-19 biri hejuru mu ntara zitandukanye z'Ubushinwa aho imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa yakoreshejwe ku barwayi 87% harimo Gansu (63.7%), Ningxia (50%) na Hunan (50%), mu gihe intara ya Hubei, aho imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa yakoreshejwe ku barwayi 30% gusa ba COVID-19, ifite igipimo cyo gukira kiri hasi cyane (13%).
Ariko kandi, ibyo biragoye kubigereranya, kuko hari ibindi bintu byinshi bigira ingaruka nko umubare n'uburemere bw'abarwayi bigomba kwitabwaho mu gusuzuma.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Boley Zhang na bagenzi be basohoye ubushakashatsi bagereranya uburyo bwo kuvura bw'iburengerazuba (WM) n'uburyo bwo kuvura buhuriweho n'ubuvuzi bw'iburengerazuba n'ubw'imigenzo gakondo y'Abashinwa.
Basanze igihe cyo kugarura ubushyuhe bw'umubiri, gukira no kujya mu bitaro mu itsinda ry'ubuvuzi bw'Iburengerazuba n'ubuvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa, ari gito cyane ugereranyije n'icyo mu itsinda ry'ubuvuzi bw'Iburengerazuba gusa.
Igishishikaje ni uko igipimo cy'indwara zidakira ziterwa n'ibimenyetso (kuva ku boroheje kugeza ku ndwara zikomeye) mu itsinda rya WM+TCM (umuti gakondo w'Abashinwa+umuti w'Iburengerazuba) cyari hasi cyane ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'abaganga b'Iburengerazuba gusa (7.4% ugereranyije na 46.2%), kandi igipimo cy'urupfu mu itsinda ry'abaganga b'Iburengerazuba+umuti w'Iburengerazuba na cyo cyari hasi ugereranyije n'itsinda ry'abaganga b'Iburengerazuba gusa (8.8% ugereranyije na 39%).
Ariko kandi, ubudahangarwa n'imikorere myiza y'imiti gakondo y'Abashinwa ikomeje gukenerwa gusuzumwa mu igerageza rikomeye kandi rifite ubushobozi bwo kugenzura neza.
Kugerageza kumenya uburyo bwo gukora no kumenya ingingo z'ingenzi z'uburyo bwo kuvura mu buvuzi gakondo bw'Abashinwa cyangwa, niba bishoboka, guhuza, birashishikaje kandi birashishikaje.
Abarwayi bakekwaho cyangwa bemejwe ko banduye COVID-19 akenshi bagira ubwoba bw'iki cyorezo cyandura cyane ndetse kihitana, ndetse n'abantu bashyizwe mu kato barambirwa, bakumva bari mu bwigunge kandi bafite umujinya.
Byongeye kandi, ibimenyetso by'indwara birimo umuriro mwinshi, kutagira umwuka n'umuhogo, hamwe n'ingaruka z'uburyo bwo kwivuza, harimo ibitotsi biterwa na corticosteroids, guhangayika n'uburwayi bwo mu mutwe, bishobora guterwa n'uburwayi.
Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo cya SARS, hari ibimenyetso byinshi by'indwara zo mu mutwe birimo kwiheba, guhangayika, ubwoba, guhungabana, ibimenyetso byo mu mutwe, guhungabana ndetse no kwiyahura.
Gukurikirana abantu no kubagenera akato, nk'igice cy'igisubizo cy'ubuzima rusange ku cyorezo cya COVID-19, bishobora gutuma abantu banduye bahangayika kandi bakumva bafite ikosa bitewe n'ingaruka z'ubwandu, kubagenera akato n'ibibazo by'imibereho y'imiryango n'incuti.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu barwaye COVID-19, abakekwaho ubwandu n'abahuye na bo, ndetse n'abaturage bose bakeneye ubu bufasha, bagomba guhabwa ubuvuzi bwo mu mutwe.
Ubufasha bw'imiti y'imitekerereze bugomba kuba bukubiyemo gushyiraho amatsinda y'ubuzima bwo mu mutwe afite ubumenyi bwinshi, gutanga amakuru asobanutse neza kandi ahamye ku cyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 no gutegura gahunda z'ubuvuzi, hamwe no gukoresha ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki n'imikorere y'amagambo mu kwirinda guhura n'abandi.
Inkingo z'ingirakamaro ni ingenzi mu guhagarika uruziga rw'ubwandu kuva ku matungo yanduye no ku bantu, kugeza ku bantu bafite ubwandu, kandi akenshi zikoreshwa nk'inkunga mu kuvura virusi mu kurwanya ibyorezo biterwa na virusi zigenda zivuka.
Hakozwe ingamba zo gukora inkingo zishingiye kuri poroteyine ya S mu rwego rwo gukora insoro z'igihe kirekire kandi zikora neza mu kurwanya SARS-CoV.
Inkingo z'ubuzima zisigaye zigiye zigeragezwa ku bikoko mu kurwanya SARS.
Ariko, mbere yuko icyigisho cy'ubuvuzi gitangira, ubushobozi bwa in-vivo bw'abakandida b'inkingo mu nguge n'inguge z'abazima n'uburyo bwo kuzirinda kwandura virusi ya Zeonusi bugomba kumenyekana.
Ibi bishobora kuba biterwa nuko SARS imaze imyaka 17 itarandura, kandi nta kindi cyorezo cyigeze kivugwa kuva icyo gihe.
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, udutsiko tw'inyamaswa tw'inyamaswa z'inkazi n'utundi dutwi tw'inyamaswa tw'inkazi na zo ziracyariho mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati, kandi ziracyaboneka mu tundi turere bitewe n'uko umutungo wa Zeonusi ukomeza kuba mu duce tw'aho.
Uburyo bwo gukingira bukoresha virusi itagikora, plasmides za DNA, virusi, nanoparticules, particules zo hafi ya virusi na protini zo mu bwoko bwa neutrecyclic byatangiye gukorwa kuri MERS, kandi mu bice bimwe byageragejwe ku nyamaswa.
Gushyiraho urukingo rwiza kandi rwiza rwa SARS-CoV-2 ku bantu bafite ubumuga ni ibintu byihutirwa kandi by'ingenzi mu kurwanya icyorezo.
Ariko, guhangana n'iki kibazo biragoye kubera igihe kirekire gikenewe mu gukora no gukora inkingo (ku kigereranyo amezi 18) no guhinduka kwa virusi ya corona.
Kubera ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, imaze igihe gito itangiye kugaragaza ibimenyetso by'uburwayi mu barwayi ibihumbi.
Mu bihe byinshi, abarwayi barakira buhoro buhoro kandi nta ngaruka z'ibyago.
Ariko, kimwe na SARS na MERS, COVID-19 ifitanye isano no kurwara cyane no gupfa mu bantu barwaye cyane.
Ku bw'ibyo, guhanga uburyo bwo kugenzura indwara ni ingenzi cyane ku bigo by'ubuvuzi kugira ngo bitange serivisi zibanze, cyane cyane mu turere dufite amikoro make.
Dukurikije ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu, ibintu bikurikira bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bipimo by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 cyangwa bifitanye isano na byo (Imbonerahamwe ya 3):
Imyaka: Imyaka ni kimwe mu bintu by'ingenzi cyane mu kwemeza ko SARS ishobora kwaduka, kimwe na COVID-19.
COVID-19 yibasira cyane cyane abantu bafite imyaka iri hagati ya 65 na 30, aho 47.7% by'abarwayi bari hejuru y'imyaka 50 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe ku barwayi 8,866 bavuzwe haruguru bayanduye.
Abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane barwara indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi no kurwara indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi kandi bafite imyaka myinshi ugereranyije n'abatarakeneye kwitabwaho cyane (imyaka 66 ugereranyije na 51), ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko imyaka ishobora gufatwa nk'ikintu cyerekana ingaruka z'abarwayi ba COVID-19.
Igitsina: Nkuko twabivuze haruguru, SARS-CoV-2 yandura abagabo cyane kurusha abagore (0,31 kuri 100,000 ugereranyije na 0,27 kuri 100,000).
Indwara n'ibibazo: Abarwayi banduye COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho cyane, barushaho kurwara umutima cyane cyangwa se umutima ukabura imbaraga.
Indwara z'umutima kandi ni zo zatumaga abantu benshi bapfa bazize SARS.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwifatanya na Clancyte z'indwara ya ACE2-positive, bishobora gutera ibibazo by'ubuhumekero mu barwayi ba COVID-19.
Ni ngombwa kuzirikana ko imyaka n'uburwayi bw'ibanze bifitanye isano ikomeye kandi bishobora guhura.
Ibimenyetso bidasanzwe bya laboratwari: Igipimo cya poroteyine C mu maraso kigaragaza uburemere bw'ubuhumekero cyangwa kwangirika kw'imyakura, kandi cyatanzwe nk'ikintu gishobora kugaragaza indwara, gusubiza imiti no gukira.
Hari ibitekerezo bivuga ko hari isano hagati y'urugero rwa CRP n'uburemere bwa COVID-19 n'uko ishobora kwanduza.
Byongeye kandi, kongera ibipimo bya lactate dehydrogenase (LDH), aspartate aminotransferase (AST), alanine aminotransferase (ALT) na creatine kinase (CK) nabyo bishobora kugira ingaruka mu kwemeza ibisubizo.
Izi enzymes zivugwa cyane mu bice bitandukanye by'umubiri, cyane cyane mu mutima n'umwijima, kandi zisohoka mu gihe habayeho kwangirika kw'umubiri.
Ku bw'ibyo, ni ibimenyetso bisanzwe byerekana indwara z'umutima cyangwa impyiko.
Ibimenyetso by'ingenzi by'uburwayi: Kugira ngo harebwe ingaruka n'ingaruka z'indwara ya COVID-19, hakwiye gufatwa ingamba zo kureba ibimenyetso by'uburwayi mu gihe cy'igihe, hamwe n'ibindi bibazo bijyanye na byo.
Gukoresha Steroids: Nkuko byavuzwe haruguru, Steroids ni imiti igabanya ubudahangarwa bw'umubiri, ikoreshwa nk'umuti wunganira mu kugabanya ubukana bw'ibikomere by'ubuhumekero mu kurwanya indwara zandura.
Kubera ko ibipimo byinshi bya corticosteroids byakoreshejwe cyane ku barwayi barwaye SARS ikomeye, abenshi mu barokotse barwaye rubagimpande ziterwa no kutagira amaraso, ubumuga bw'igihe kirekire n'ubuzima budafite agaciro.
Ku bw'ibyo, niba ari ngombwa, abarwayi ba COVID-19 bagomba guhabwa steroid mu gipimo cyo hasi kandi mu gihe gito.
Umunaniro wo mu mutwe: Nk'uko byavuzwe haruguru, abantu benshi bari barwaye COVID-19 bahangayitse cyane kubera ko akenshi babaga bategetswe kumara igihe kirekire mu kato, bakagira amakenga menshi, bakumva ko nta cyo bazi ku byabaye, kandi bakibonera urupfu rw'abagize umuryango wabo cyangwa inshuti zabo za bugufi.
Gutanga ubujyanama mu by'imitekerereze n'ubufasha bw'igihe kirekire ni ngombwa mu gufasha abo barwayi guhangana n'imihangayiko no gusubira mu buzima busanzwe.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe kugeza ubu bugaragaza ko COVID-19 ifite ibimenyetso bitandukanye n'iby'icyorezo cya SARS.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwiyongera mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, kimwe n'izindi koronavirusi zitera ibicurane bisanzwe, ikongera mu nzira y'ubuhumekero yo hejuru, kandi ikagaragara mu ntangiriro z'icyiciro cy'ubwandu, igaragaza ibimenyetso byoroheje cyangwa nta bimenyetso.
Ku bw'ibyo, abarwayi banduye mu gihe cy'ibanze cyangwa mu gihe cy'ihungabana bashobora gukora virusi nyinshi mu bikorwa byabo bya buri munsi, bigatuma bigorana kugenzura icyorezo.
Icyakora, ibyagezweho byerekana ko SARS-CoV yandura mu gihe abarwayi bari mu cyiciro gikomeye cy'uburwayi, bityo rero, ibyinshi mu byiciro by'ubwandu ntibyabaga mu cyiciro cya mbere.
Ku bw'ibyo, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kiriho ubu kirakomeye kandi kiragoye kugenzura kurusha icyorezo cya SARS.
Mu Bushinwa hari ibikorwa byiza birimo kugenzura neza kwinjira no gusohoka mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'imidugudu ihakikije, no gushyira mu kato abaturage hafi ya bose, mu rwego rwo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya SARS-CoV-2.
Nubwo ibi byagize ingaruka zikomeye ku bukungu n'ibindi bice by'igihugu, umubare w'abarwayi bashya uragabanuka, bikaba bigaragaza ko icyorezo kirimo kugabanuka.
Ubushakashatsi buvuga ko iki cyorezo kizarangira muri Werurwe, kandi ko icyiciro cyo kugenzura kizamara amezi atatu kugeza kuri ane.
Ariko kandi, hari abahanga batagira icyizere.
Paul Hunter na bagenzi be, batangaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19, cyandura cyane kurusha SARS, kitazarangira mu 2020.
Ira Langini na bagenzi be bakoze uburyo bwo guhanura ingaruka z'icyorezo, batanga igitekerezo cy'uko virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kwanduza bibiri bya gatatu by'abatuye isi.
Itsinda ry'abashakashatsi bo muri Kanada batangaje ko SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu byiciro byombi by'ibipimo by'imyanda yo mu mazuru n'izuru mu barwayi bakize nyuma y'ibyumweru bibiri basohotse ibitaro.
Ariko kandi, hari icyizere cyinshi mu Bushinwa bitewe n'igabanuka ry'ubwandu bushya, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko ingamba z'ubu zigiye kugera ku ntego.
Mu mizo ya mbere, byatekerezwaga ko Ebola ishobora kwandura abantu bagera kuri miliyoni imwe, igahitana abagera kuri miliyoni eshanu.
Icyakora, icyorezo cyaje kugenzurwa binyuze mu kucyirinda no kucyitandukanya n'ibindi.
Kimwe na SARS-CoV, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugenda igabanuka buhoro buhoro, hanyuma ikazazimira cyangwa ikahinduka virusi idafite ubwandu bwinshi, ikabana n'abantu.
Gereranya icyorezo cya COVID-19 na SARS na MERS byerekanwe hepfo (Igishushanyo cya 5).
SARS-CoV-2 ikwirakwira cyane mu gihe umuntu akoroye cyangwa atetse, kandi ishobora no gukwirakwira mu gihe ahuriye n'ikintu cyanduza virusi.
Iyi virusi kandi yagaragaye mu bintu byanduye, bituma bishoboka ko umuntu ashobora guhita yandura virusi itera SIDA.
Ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa ku barwayi 138 bwagaragaje ko 41% by'abarwayi bashobora kuba baranduye indwara z'ibitaro, harimo 17 barwaye izindi ndwara n'abandi 40 bakora mu buvuzi.
Ku bw'ibyo, abantu bagomba kwitondera cyane cyane abakozi b'ubuzima, abakozi b'imiryango, abagize umuryango, abakozi bakorana ndetse n'abasuye abarwayi banduye cyangwa abantu banduye.
Uburyo bwa mbere bwo kwirinda virusi ni ukwambara udupfukamunwa tw'amaso, tw'ubwoko bw'imashini zo guhumeka n'udupfukamunwa tw'imashini zo kubaga (N95 series number 1860s) kugira ngo tugabanya ibyago byo kwandura.
Udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi turinda gutwara mu mwuka ibitonyanga by'amazi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero biva mu gice cy'umugongo gishobora kuba cyanduye bikagera ku bandi cyangwa bikamanika ku bice by'umubiri hanyuma bikagera ku bandi.
Ariko, udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bwa N95 (numero y'ubwoko bwa 1860s) dushobora kurinda umuntu guhumeka virusi ziri hagati ya 10 na 80 nanometero, aho virusi 5% gusa zishobora kwinjira; virusi ya SARS-CoV-2 ifite ingano nk'iya SARS-CoV, kandi zombi zifite ingano ya 85 nanometero.
Kubera ko udukoko dushobora guturukira ku masike eshanu z'ubuvuzi, abavura abarwayi bagombye gukoresha udupfukamunwa twa N95 (serie 1860s) kandi bakirinda kwambara udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi.
Uretse udupfukamunwa, abakozi b'ubuzima bagomba kwambara imyenda yihariye ikingira umubiri wose kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago byo guhura na virusi.
Virusi kandi ishobora kwanduza umuntu binyuze mu jisho.
Ku ya 22 Mutarama 2020, umuganga yanduye SARS-CoV-2 igihe yari yambaye agapfukamunwa ka N95, bikaba bishoboka ko yanduye binyuze mu jisho rye ryanduye.
Ku bw'ibyo, abavura abarwayi bagomba gukoresha indorerwamo cyangwa amadarubindi mu gihe bakira abarwayi.
Mu rwego rwo kwita ku buzima rusange mu duce twanduye cyangwa dushobora kwandura, abantu barasabwa gukaraba intoki kenshi bakoresheje isabune yica udukoko, kwihererana no kuguma mu rugo no kugabanya guhura n'abantu bashobora kwandura.
Umuntu wese agomba kugendera kure y'undi afite uburebure bwa metero imwe n'igice.
Ibi bikorwa bifatwa nk'uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ndetse no gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Nubwo SARS-CoV-2 izwi nk'indwara nshya ku bantu, isano ikomeye ifitanye na SARS-CoV, yatangajwe ku ya 7 Mutarama 2020, yatumye Ubushinwa butabura guhangayika, bituma abantu bibuka icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2003.
Ariko, nta gikorwa cyo guhumuriza abantu cyakozwe kugeza tariki ya 19 Mutarama 2020, ubwo umuyobozi w'ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara cya Wuhan yatangazaga ko virusi nshya ifite ubukana buke kandi ko ishobora kwanduzanya mu buryo bworoshye kandi ko ishobora gukingirwa.
Ubwo butumwa bwatumye abantu batafata iyo miburo nk'ukuri, cyane cyane mu gihe igihugu cyose cyari kigiye kwizihiza Umunsi Mukuru w'Ubunani, bityo bibabuza uburyo bw'ingenzi bwo gukumira ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Ibigo bishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu Bushinwa bishobora kuba byaravanye isomo rikomeye kuri iki kibazo, bigakora n'amavugurura y'ingenzi mu ngamba z'igihe kizaza.
