Inkomoko y'inyamaswa za HCoVs
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, ihinduka ry'imiterere n'ihindagurika ry'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byafashije koronavirus (CoVs) n'abanduye muri zo guhinduka icyarimwe, harimo n'abantu.
Mbere ya 2003, abantu babiri bafite virusi itera SIDA (HCoV) bari bazwiho gutera indwara zidakomeye, nk'indwara y'igicuri.
Icyorezo cy'indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye (SARS) na MERS (Middle East Respiratory Syndrome) byashyize ku yindi ngingo y'ibiceri, byerekana ko bishobora kwangiza no guteza akaga k'ubwandu bwa coronavirus.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye mu Bushinwa rwagati mu mpera za 2019, ituma koronavirusi yongera kugaragara cyane, idutangaza kubera ubukana bwayo, ariko ikagira ubwandu buciriritse ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
Indwara ya HCoV ifite inkomoko mu nyamaswa (zoonosis), kandi kumenya inkomoko y'inyamaswa ya HCoVs biradufasha cyane.
Benshi muri ba HCoV batangira guterwa n'imbeba, kandi nta bwandu butera.
Hari kandi abarwayi ba virusi ya coronavirusi zimwe na zimwe bazwiho kuba ari ba nyirabayazana ba virusi ya coronavirusi.
Kumenya inyamaswa z'abashyitsi bifasha mu buryo butaziguye mu gukumira indwara z'abantu.
Ubushakashatsi ku mikoranire ya COV mu matungo bushobora kuduha amakuru y'ingenzi ku bijyanye n'ubwandu mu bantu.
Muri ubu bushakashatsi, turatanga isesengura ry'amakuru kuri koronavirusi zirindwi zahumani, twibanda ku mateka y'ubushakashatsi bwazo, inkomoko y'inyamaswa n'ubwandu bw'ubwoko.
Icy'ingenzi kurushaho, turagereranya kandi turwanya COVID-19 zitandukanye mu buryo bw'ihindagurika rya virusi na genome.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) kivugwa muri iyi nkuru.
Byongeye kandi, ibintu bikenewe kugira ngo umuntu agere ku ntego mu kwimuka hagati y'abamugaye n'ibimenyetso by'ihindagurika rya virusi ku buremere bw'indwara na byo byibanzeho.
Coronaviruses (CoVs) ni zo zigize umuryango wa Coronaviridae, ugizwe n'itsinda ry'udukoko tugize RNA tw'uruhu rumwe (sino-positive).
" Izi virusi zifite genome nini cyane iri hagati ya kilobes 26 na 32 muri virusi za RNA, zitiriwe "CoVs (coronavirus) " cyangwa virusi z'igiti kubera imiterere yazo nk'iy'ingori ku mikorosikopi ya elegitoroniki".
Mu miterere, koronavirusi zifite genome imwe ifite imiterere isa.
Hafi bibiri bya gatatu bya genome birimo ibipimo bibiri byanditseho byanditseho (ORF1a na ORF1b) bisobanurwa nk'ibisobanuro bya poroteyine pp1a na pp1ab.
Poroteyine nyinshi zikorwa kugirango zitange poroteyine 16 zitari mu miterere zitwa nsp1 kugeza 16.
Poroteyine y'ibisigazwa bya jenome irimo ORFs ya poroteyine z'imiterere, harimo spike (S), virus cover (E), membrane (M) na nucleoprotein (N).
Poroteyine nyinshi z'inkomoko zigaragazwa n'ubwoko butandukanye bwa koronavirusi.
Kubera itandukaniro ry'imiterere ya poroteyine, coronaviruses igabanyijemo amoko ane (alpha coronaviruses, beta coronaviruses, gamma coronaviruses na delta coronaviruses) muri yo, genus beta ya coronaviruses ikubiyemo benshi muri human coronaviruses kandi igabanyijemo amoko ane mato (A, B, C na D).
Ibihamya bya phylogenetic byerekana ko udusimba n'imbeba ari byo bitanga inkomoko y'ibinyabuzima bya CoVs nyinshi za alpha na beta, mu gihe inyoni ari zo zitanga amakuru y'ibinyabuzima bya CoVs byinshi bya Gamma na Delta.
Mu myaka ibarirwa mu bihumbi, koronavirusi zakomeje kunyura mu nzitizi z'amoko, zimwe muri zo zigaragara nk'indwara zikomeye ku bantu.
Kugeza ubu, hamaze kumenyekana ubwoko burindwi bwa HCoVs.
Muri izo virusi harimo HCoV-229E na HCoV-NL63, ari zo alfa-CoVs.
Izindi coronavirusi eshanu za beta zirimo HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1, SARS-CoV, MERS na SARS-CoV-2.
HCoV-229E, HCoV-OC43, HCoV-HKU1 na HCoV-NL63 akenshi zitera ibimenyetso byoroheje nk'uburwayi bworoheje n'/cyangwa iseseme.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'ubwo, SARS-CoV, MERS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 ziherutse kumenyekana ni indwara ziterwa n'ubwandu bwinshi, kandi mu barwayi benshi ziteza indwara zikomeye zo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yo hasi, kandi zituma ibyago byo kurwara indwara y'ubuhumekero (ARDS) n'ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero byiyongera cyane.
Ubwoko bwa mbere bwa HCoV-229E, B814, bwadukuwe mu muhogo w'inzoka mu barwayi banduye iki cyorezo mu myaka ya za 60.
