Icyakora, icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) ni indwara nshya, kandi ubumenyi bwacu bugenda bwiyongera bufatiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye mu buvuzi.
Muri iyi baruwa, twashubije ku gitekerezo cyatanzwe ku buyobozi bwacu, kandi dutanga ibipimo bishya byemewe n'amategeko yo gusuzuma abantu bakekwaho COVID-19 nk'uko biteganywa n'amabwiriza mashya yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 (Inyandiko ya karindwi) yatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima ya Repubulika y'Ubushinwa.
Mu Ukuboza 2019, coronavirus nshya ya 2019 (2019-nCoV) yatumye habaho icyorezo cy'indwara, ubu cyitwa coronavirus disease 2019 (COVID-19) na coronavirus ya syndrome respiratoire aiguësse.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe 2020, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2, itsinda ryacu ryateguye amabwiriza yihuse yo gutanga inama yashyizwe ku rubuga rwa interineti ku itariki ya 6 Gashyantare 2020 mu bushakashatsi bw'ubuvuzi bwa gisirikare (Military Medical Research).
Ibi byateje impagarara nyinshi kuva byandikwa.
Zirikana ko COVID-19 ari indwara nshya, kandi ko ubumenyi bwacu buzajya buzamuka buhoro buhoro, dushingiye ku bushakashatsi bukomeje gukorwa n'ubunararibonye bw'abaganga.
Urugero, amabwiriza yo gusuzuma no kuvura COVID-19 yatanzwe na Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'Ubushinwa (http://www.nhc.gov.cn/), yashyizwe ahagaragara mu byiciro birindwi kuva ku ya 16 Mutarama 2020 kugeza ku ya 3 Werurwe 2020, bimwe mu bikubiye muri ayo mabwiriza bikaba byarahindutse.
Ubu, amabwiriza yacu yahawe ibitekerezo na Xu na bagenzi be, batanze igitekerezo cyoroshye cyo gutanga amanota hashingiwe ku buhanga bwabo mu buvuzi.
Ibikorwa byabo byongereye ibimenyetso bishya ku buyobozi bwacu kandi bikomeza gutanga ibisobanuro byingenzi kuri iki cyorezo ku isi hose.
Turabashimira kandi turabashimira ku bw'imihati ikomeye bashyizeho.
Ariko kandi, hakurikijwe uburyo bushya bwo gupima no kuvura COVID-19 (igitabo cya karindwi cy'igerageza) n'ubushakashatsi buherutse gukorwa, ibyo bakora na byo bikeneye kuvugururwa.
Mu isesengura rya karindwi (3 Werurwe 2020), kugira ngo umuntu akomeze kuba umuganga, buri kintu cyose cy'amateka y'icyorezo kigomba guhuzwa n'ibintu bibiri by'ibimenyetso byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi kugira ngo habeho isesengura ryuzuye, cyangwa mu gihe nta mateka y'icyorezo ahari, hagomba kuba hari ibintu bitatu by'ibimenyetso byo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi:
Amateka y'icyorezo: (1) amateka y'urugendo cyangwa kuba mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije cyangwa mu tundi duce tw'abaturage aho abantu banduye COVID-19 batangajwe mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (2) amateka y'abakoze ibizamini bya SARS-CoV-2 (binyuze mu gupima nucleic acid neza); (3) amateka y'abakoze ibizamini by'abarwayi bafite umuriro cyangwa ibimenyetso byo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan n'uturere tuwukikije cyangwa mu tundi turere COVID-19 yatangariwemo mu minsi 14 ishize mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira kugaragara; (4) amateka y'abakoze ibizamini by'abantu banduye COVID-19 byemejwe (abantu 2 banduye umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso by'ubuhumekero mu cyumweru mu duce duto nk'inzu, aho bakorera, mu ishuri, n'ibindi).
Ibimenyetso by'uburwayi: (1) umuriro n'/cyangwa ibimenyetso byo guhumeka. (2) Kuba afite ibimenyetso byerekana ubwandu bwa COVID-19; (3) Umubare w'amaraso y'umweru yose, mu ntangiriro y'igihe cy'uburwayi, mu cyiciro cy'umubare usanzwe, cyangwa se kugabanuka kw'imyanya y'amaraso.
Gushakisha byemejwe bigomba kuba bishingiye ku muntu ukekwaho ubwandu bw'indwara cyangwa indwara z'amaraso nk'uko bikurikira: (1) ibipimo bya PCR mu gihe nyacyo bya SARS-CoV-2 byerekana ko afite virusi; (2) urutonde rwa virusi yose yerekana ko ifite virusi nshya ya CoV; (3) igisubizo cyiza ku rukingo rw'umubiri rukoreshwa mu kurwanya IgM na IgG mu gupima SARS-CoV-2 mu iseru; cyangwa impinduka y'urukingo rwa IgG rwatanzwe kuri SARS-CoV-2 kuva ku mbi kugera ku nziza, cyangwa kwiyongera kwa tetrisite inshuro 4 cyangwa zirenze mu gihe cyo gukira kurenze icyo kigero mu cyiciro gikomeye.
Dushobora kubona ko ibizamini bya PCR by'akanya gato, bya nucleic acid mu myanya y'ubuhumekero cyangwa ibipimo by'amaraso, byongerewe ku mpinduka ya kabiri (18 Mutarama 2020) n'iya gatatu (22 Mutarama 2020).
Ibipimo by'amaraso by'ubwandu byongerewe ku nshuro ya kane (27 Mutarama 2020) no ku ya gatanu (8 Gashyantare 2020); nyuma ibimenyetso bya seroloji byongerewe ku nshuro ya karindwi.
