Ibikoresho byo gupfuka mu gihe cyo kubaga birakwiriye ku bantu bashobora kuba baranduye kuko bishobora kugabanya ubunini n'intera y'ibitonyanga byo mu mwuka umuntu aterera mu gihe avuga, gusinzira no gukorora.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatanze amabwiriza yerekeranye n'igihe n'uburyo bwo kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Stephen Griffin, impuguke mu by'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa virusi muri Kaminuza ya Leeds, yavuze ko "kwambara agapfukamunwa bishobora kugabanya ubushake bw'abantu bwo gukora ku maso, kuko ari byo bituma abantu benshi banduza".
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryasabye abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza gukoresha udupfukamunwa gusa mu gihe bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura, urugero nko kwita ku bantu barwaye COVID-19, nubwo ryemeza ko gukoresha udupfukamunwa bishobora gufasha abantu kwirinda gukorakora mu maso.
Ibihugu byinshi byatangiye gushishikariza abaturage gukoresha udupfukamunwa.
Muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, CDC itera inkunga gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubwanwa twakozwe mu myenda. Mu Bushinwa, abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza mu baturage, cyane cyane mu gihe bahuye n'abandi bantu bari hafi ya metero 1 (ibirenge 3 cyangwa munsi yayo), baterwa inkunga yo gukoresha udupfukamunwa tw'ubwoko bumwe.
Hong Kong irasaba ko abantu bakoresha udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari mu modoka zitwara abagenzi cyangwa mu duce dutuwe n'abantu benshi.
Abashinzwe ubuzima muri Thailand barimo gushishikariza abantu gukora udupfukamunwa tw'impu mu ngo zabo no gukaraba imyenda yabo buri munsi.
Repubulika ya Tchécoslovaquie yatangaje ko abantu batemerewe kujya mu ruhame batambaye agapfukamunwa cyangwa udupfukamunwa.
Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Vietnam yasabye abantu bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari ahantu hahurira abantu benshi kugira ngo birinde n'abandi.
Leta ya Autriche yasabye abantu kwinjira mu maduka y'ibyokurya kwambara udupfukamunwa.
Israel yasabye abaturage bayo bose kwambara udupfukamunwa mu gihe bari ahantu hahurira abantu benshi.
Taiwan, imaze kugera ku bushobozi bwo gukora udupfukamunwa miliyoni icumi ku munsi kuva mu kwezi kwa gatatu, yasabye ko abakinnyi b'amagare n'amabisi y'imbere mu mujyi bakoresha udupfukamunwa guhera ku ya 1 Mata.
Muri Panama, gukoresha agapfukamunwa ni ngombwa iyo ugiye hanze, kandi abadashobora kubona agapfukamunwa bagomba kugakora mu rugo.
Udupfukamunwa twakoreshejwe cyane mu Buyapani, Koreya y'Epfo, Malaysia na Singapore.
Kwirinda kwegerana (nanone bizwi ku izina ry'irinde kurwana) bikubiyemo ingamba zo kurwanya ubwandu zigamije kugabanya ubwandu binyuze mu kugabanya guhura kw'abantu ku buryo budahagije.
Muri izo ngamba harimo guhagarika abantu mu ngo zabo, guhagarika ingendo, no guhagarika amashuri, aho bakorera, ibibuga by'imikino, za sitade cyangwa ibigo by'ubucuruzi.
Abantu bashobora kubahiriza intera hagati yabo mu gihe bagumye mu rugo, bakirinda ingendo, birinda ahantu hari abantu benshi, bakoresha uburyo bwo guhanahana amakuru nta muntu uhuye na we kandi bakirinda gutandukana n'abandi.
Ibihugu byinshi byamaze gushyiraho cyangwa bigatanga inama yo kwirinda abantu mu duce twashyizwe mu kato, aho iyi ndwara yageze.
Umubare munini w'abaturage baturuka mu baturage, ugereranyije n'abategetsi n'inzego z'ubuzima muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, wavuye ku bantu 250 (niba nta muntu urwaye COVID-19 muri ako gace) ugera kuri 50 hanyuma ukagera ku bantu 10.
Kuva ku ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwashyizeho itegeko ribuza abantu benshi guhurira hamwe. Abantu bafite ibibazo by'uburwayi nk'indwara ya diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko ukabije w'amaraso n'uburwayi bw'umubiri bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara z'ubuhumekero bukabije n'izindi ndwara ziterwa na zo, kandi bagombye kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka mu duce twiganjemo abantu benshi nk'uko CDC ibisaba. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima bahinduye ijambo "intera rusange" barigira "intera isanzwe" kugira ngo bagaragaze niba intego yabo ari ukugabanya guhura mu buryo bwa 'virtual' cyangwa se mu buryo bwa kure.
" Gukoresha ijambo ""kwirinda gutandukana kw'abantu"" byakuyeho igitekerezo cy'uko abantu bagomba kwifatanya mu kwihererana mu buryo bw'inyongera aho kubashishikariza gushyikirana n'abandi mu bundi buryo. Hari abayobozi batanze amabwiriza y'isuku y'imibonano mpuzabitsina muri iki cyorezo. "
Muri ibyo harimo inama yo kugirana imibonano mpuzabitsina n'uwo mwashakanye udafite ibimenyetso bya virusi.
Abantu banduye COVID-19 n'abakekwaho ubwandu basabwe kwiherera.
Ibigo by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye ku buryo bwo kwitarura abantu. Leta nyinshi zategetse cyangwa zasabye ko abantu bose batuye mu duce twanduye bagomba kwitarura abantu.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwisanzura yashyizweho ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bahuye n'umuntu wanduye COVID-19 n'abaherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere kiganjemo icyorezo, basabwe kwiherera mu kato iminsi 14 uhereye igihe baherukaga guhura.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya ubwandu bw'indwara burimo kugabanya cyangwa kugabanya ubwandu.
Ingamba zo kwirinda indwara zishyirwa mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, hagamijwe gukurikirana no gushyira abantu banduye mu kato, no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kurwanya indwara no gukingira kugira ngo bareke gukwirakwiza indwara ku bandi bantu.
Iyo bitagishoboka kwirinda ko indwara itangira, imihati ijya mu cyiciro cyo kugabanya: ingamba zo kugabanya umuvuduko wo gukwirakwira kwa virusi no kugabanya ingaruka zayo ku buzima n'abaturage.
Hari igihe hashyirwaho uburyo bwo guhagarika no kugabanya ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi.
Gukumira iki cyorezo bisaba ingamba zikomeye kugira ngo umubare w'abandura w'icyorezo ugere munsi ya 1. Kimwe mu byo umuntu yakora mu gucunga icyorezo ni ukugabanya umubare w'abanduye, ibyo bikaba byitwa no guhanagura ibipimo by'icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo kuremererwa cyane mu buvuzi kandi bigatuma haboneka igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibipimo by'ubutabazi bitagamije imiti bishobora kugenzura ikwirakwira rya virusi birimo ingamba zo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nk'isuku y'intoki, kwambara agapfukamunwa no kwitarura abantu; ingamba rusange zo kwirinda abantu, nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika ibikorwa rusange; uruhare rw'abaturage mu gushishikariza abantu kwemera no kwitabira ibyo bikorwa; ndetse n'ingamba z'ibidukikije, nko gusukura aho hantu. Ingamba zikomeye cyane zo gukumira icyorezo mu Bushinwa zashyizwe mu bikorwa igihe iki cyorezo cyagaragaye ko gikomeye, nko gushyira mu kato imigi yose no kubuza ingendo.
Ibihugu byinshi byateye intambwe zitandukanye mu rwego rwo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yatangiye kugenzura abaturage no gushyira abantu mu kato, kandi igabisha abantu ku birebana n'ingendo n'ingendo z'abanduye.
Singapore yatanze inkunga y'amafaranga ku bantu banduye biyemeje kwihererana kandi itegeka ibihano bikomeye ku bantu birengagiza kwihererana.
Taiwan yongereye ingano y'udupfukamunwa kandi ishyiraho ibihano bikomeye ku bantu batanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. Imyitozo yo kugereranya yakozwe ku Bwongereza na Amerika yagaragaje ko kugabanya icyorezo (kugabanya cyangwa kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo) no kugabanya (kugabanya umuvuduko w'icyorezo) ari imbogamizi zikomeye.
Amategeko yo kugabanya ingano y'ibikomere ashobora kugabanya umubare w'abasaba serivisi z'ubuzima ku kigero cya 2/3 n'abapfa ku kigero cya kimwe cya kabiri, ariko akomeza gutuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa kandi ubushobozi bw'ubuvuzi bukaba burenze ubushobozi.
Gukumira bishobora gukorwa, ariko bigomba gukomeza igihe cyose virusi ikomeje gukwirakwira hagati y'abantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rumaze gukorwa, ibiba bitangiye), bitabaye ibyo, igihe ingamba zikaze zizagabanuka, virusi izongera igere ku rwego rwo hejuru kandi ikwirakwizwe.
Kugira ngo haboneke uburyo bwo guhangana n'icyorezo mu gihe kirekire, bisaba amafaranga menshi mu rwego rw'ubukungu n'imibereho.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi wemejwe wa COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa birimo kugerageza imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti igabanya uburibwe, kunywa amazi n'ikiruhuko bishobora gufasha mu kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'uburemere, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko haboneka imiti ikoreshwa mu guhumeka, umwuka wa ogisijeni, amazi yo mu mitsi n'ubufasha mu guhumeka.
Gukoresha steroid bishobora gutuma indwara irushaho gukomera.
Imiti myinshi yari isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura izindi ndwara zituruka kuri virusi iri gusuzumwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko hari "imiti isanzwe n'iy'iwacu" ishobora kugabanya ibibazo biterwa na SARS-COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryemeje ko kongera ubushobozi no gushyira mu bikorwa serivisi z'ubuvuzi mu guhangana n'ibikenewe n'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ari ingamba z'ingenzi mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ikigo cy'u Burayi Gishinzwe Kurwanya no Kurinda Indwara (ECDC) n'ibiro by'akarere k'u Burayi by'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS), byatanze amabwiriza ku bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo bihindure ibikoresho ku byiciro bitandukanye, harimo kwibanda ku bikorwa by'amavuriro mu gupima COVID-19, gukuraho uburyo bwo gupima aho bishoboka, gushyira mu kato abarwayi bafite COVID-19 no kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku barwayi bababaye cyane binyuze mu kwigisha abakozi no kongera umubare w'ibyuma bihumeka n'ibitanda.
Hari ibitekerezo bitandukanye ku muntu wa mbere wanduye (witwa Patient Number Zero).
Umuntu wa mbere uzwiho coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba yarapfuye tariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, Hubei n'ahandi mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubei wagendaga wiyongera.
Benshi muri bo bari mu isoko ry'ibyokurya byo mu nyanja rya Hunan, aho bagurishirizaga inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo cy'uko iyi virusi yavuye muri izo nyamaswa, cyangwa se ko ikomoka ku nyamaswa. Ibiribwa byanduye indwara y'ibihaha n'amahembe (pneumonia) z'impamvu zitazwi byavumbuwe ku ya 26 Ukuboza, kandi byitabirwa na muganga Zhang Jixiang mu bitaro by'intara ya Hubei, kandi byamenyeshejwe ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara cya Xianang mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 27 Ukuboza.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bikuru bya Wuhan baburiye bagenzi babo ko hari "coronavirus imeze nka SARS".
Abaganga umunani barimo Li Wenliang, barashakishwaga n'abapolisi kubera gukwirakwiza ibihuha, undi muganga witwa Ifen, yacyashwe n'abamusumba kubera ko yari yongeyeho igipimo cyo kwitwararika.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan yaje gushyira ahagaragara itangazo rusange ku ya 31 Ukuboza, imenyesha OMS.
Umubare munini w'abarwaye pneumonia bataramenyekana batangajwe ku bayobozi b'ubuzima mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntangiriro za Mutarama, bituma hatangira iperereza. Mu ntangiriro z'icyorezo, umubare w'abarwaye wikubye kabiri hafi buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu zindi ntara z'Ubushinwa kubera ko umwaka mushya w'Ubushinwa watangiye, kandi Wuhan ikaba ari imwe mu mijyi ikomeye itwara abantu n'ibintu, ndetse n'aho imihanda y'indarayi ihuza.
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko hari abantu bashya 140 banduye, barimo babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Nyuma, amakuru yemewe yerekana ko kugeza ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020, abantu 6174 bari bafite ibimenyetso by'indwara. Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarenze Ubushinwa n'Ubutaliyani ku mubare munini w'abanduye isi. Kugeza ku ya 9 Mata 2020, abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 bari baranduye ku isi hose; abantu barenga 97,000 barapfuye, abarenga 364,000 barakize.
Mu bihugu n'uturere bigera kuri 200, nibura hari umuntu umwe wanduye.
Kubera icyorezo cyugarije u Burayi, ibihugu byinshi mu karere ka Schengen byagabanyije urujya n'uruza rw'abantu kandi bishyiraho imipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu birimo ingamba zo kugabanya abantu, nko kuguma mu rugo (mu mazina y'amabwiriza yo kuguma mu rugo, amabwiriza yo kwihisha mu rugo cyangwa kugenzura burundu), no kubuza abantu kugenda. Kugeza ku ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300 muri Amerika, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abatuye isi, bari mu buryo runaka bwo kugenzura mu rugo, abasaga miliyoni 50 muri Filipine, miliyoni 59 muri Afurika y'Epfo na miliyoni 1.3 mu Buhinde bari mu buryo bw'izungura mu rugo.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi bari mu buryo runaka bwo gushyirwa mu kato, nyuma y'iminsi ibiri, uwo mubare wageze kuri miliyari 2,6, ni ukuvuga kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Umuntu wa mbere wemejwe ko yanduye COVID-19 ni uwa Wuhan ku ya 1 Ukuboza 2019; raporo zitemejwe zemeza ko umuntu wa mbere yanduye ari uwa 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr Zhang Jixian yasanze hari itsinda ry'abarwayi bafite indwara y'ibihaha ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, maze ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, ibitaro bye bihita bitangaza kuri Wuhan Jianghan Center for Disease Control.
Ibizamini bya mbere byagenewe ibipimo by'abarwayi ku ya 27 Ukuboza 2019 byerekanye ko COVID-19 imeze nka SARS.
Itangazo rusange ryatanzwe na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Umujyi wa Wuhan ku ya 31 Ukuboza.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryamenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
" Mu gutangaza ayo makuru, polisi yaburiye abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan ko bashobora kuba barimo ""gukwirakwiza ibihuha"" ku cyorezo. "
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima y'u Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "bihamya bifatika" bigaragaza ko iyi ndwara ishobora kwanduzwa n'abantu".
Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije ubukangurambaga bukomeye, nyuma yaho bushyirwa mu bikorwa n'umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti b'Ubushinwa Xi Jinping, buvugwaho ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo gukumira ikwirakwira rya virusi.
" Mu gihe cyiswe ""igikorwa gikomeye cyo kwisuzumisha mu mateka y'abantu"", ku ya 23 Mutarama hatangajwe gahunda yo gufunga abantu mu buryo bw'ubuzima, ihagarika kwinjira no gusohoka mu mujyi wa Wuhan, kandi ikwira mu mijyi 15 ya Hubei, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57 barandura".
Imodoka z'abantu ku giti cyabo zarabujijwe mu mujyi.
Iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa (25 Mutarama) yahagaritswe mu bice byinshi.
Abategetsi batangaje kandi ko hari n'ibitaro by'agateganyo byubatswe, ibitaro bya Huoshenshan, byarangiye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari ikindi bitaro byubatswe, cyitwaga Ibitaro bya Leishenshan, kugira ngo kijye kwita ku barwayi benshi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byubatswe, Ubushinwa bwongeye guhindura ibindi bigo 14 byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan nk'ibigo by'amakoraniro na za sitade, bihinduka ibitaro by'agateganyo. Ku ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho izindi ngamba zo gukumira ikwirakwira rya COVID-19, harimo gutanga ibyangombwa by'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kongera igihe cy'ikiruhuko cya Spring Festival.
Kaminuza n'amashuri na byo byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Intara ya Hong Kong na Macao zagize ingamba zitandukanye, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
Ingamba zo kwirinda abantu bari kure zashyizwe mu bikorwa mu bice bitandukanye by'u Bushinwa.
Ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo zashyizweho mu ntara ya Hubei no hanze yayo.
Ubwoko bw'ingendo rusange bwarahagaritswe, kandi inzu ndangamurage zigiye gufungwa by'agateganyo mu Bushinwa.
Mu mijyi myinshi, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abatuye isi) bakomeje gufatirwa ingamba zo kwirinda kujya hanze. Nyuma y'aho iki cyorezo kigere ku isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bashyizeho ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda ko virusi ituruka mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashyizeho gahunda yo gushyira abantu bose bavuye mu bindi bihugu mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 iyo binjiye mu mujyi. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Ubushinwa bwari bufite umuntu umwe gusa wanduye, wari waranduye mu minsi itanu ishize, ubwo yari avuye i Willeybull mu mujyi wa Guangzhou.
Ku ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Li He Chiang, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bushinwa, yatangaje ko icyorezo cy'ubwandu mu gihugu cyahagaze kandi ko icyorezo cy'iki cyorezo mu Bushinwa cyagenzurwa.
Kuri uwo munsi, ingendo mu gihugu cya Hubei, uretse i Wuhan, zaragabanyijwe nyuma y'amezi abiri hashyizweho gahunda yo kuguma mu kato. Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020 ko kwinjira mu gihugu ku baturage n'abafite viza bizaba bihagaritswe guhera ku ya 28 Werurwe, ariko ntiyatangaje igihe iyo politiki izamara.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bagomba gusaba Visa muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsula z'Ubushinwa.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yashishikarije abafite ubucuruzi n'inganda gutangira gukora guhera ku ya 30 Werurwe, ndetse itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bigo by'ubucuruzi. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi w'icyunamo rusange, ku itariki ya 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri za mu gitondo, mu gihe hazabaho iminota itatu y'agacerere mu gihugu cyose, mu gihe ibirori bya Qing Ming byari bihuje n'umunsi mukuru, nubwo leta y'igihugu yasabye imiryango ku rubuga rwa interineti gukomeza kugendera kure kugira ngo irinde icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Byaremejwe ko COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa ku ya 20 Mutarama 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima n'imiti cyatangaje ko habayeho kwiyongera gukomeye kw'abanduye ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare, ahanini biturutse ku myigaragambyo yabereye i Daegu mu rwego rw'umuteguro mushya w'idini witwa Shincheonji Church of Christ.
Abashyigikiye Shincheonji bari baje gusura Daegu i Wuhan, bakeka ko ari we watangije iyi virus.
Kuva ku ya 22 Gashyantare, ibimenyetso by'indwara byatangajwe ku bantu 1,261 cyangwa 13% mu bantu 9,336 bo muri Kiliziya. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje icyiciro cyo hejuru cy'umuburo ku ya 23 Gashyantare 2020.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abantu barenga 2000 bemejwe ko banduye muri Koreya, ku ya 29 Gashyantare, bari 3150.
Ibitaro byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko abasirikare batatu bagaragaweho coronavirus.
Gahunda ya Koreya y'Epfo ni yo ya mbere nini kandi nziza ku isi, ikaba yaragize icyo igeraho mu gupima abaturage kubera virusi no gushyira abantu mu kato, ndetse no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abo bahuye na bo.
Uburyo bwo gupima burimo kwisuzumisha ibimenyetso by'abashya ku ndege mpuzamahanga binyuze muri porogaramu za telefoni zigendanwa, gupima virusi ku modoka, ibisubizo byerekana ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20,000 ku munsi.
Nubwo gahunda ya Koreya y'Epfo itari irimo gushyira abantu mu kato mu mijyi yose, ni yo yagize icyo igeraho mu kurwanya icyorezo. Mu mizo ya mbere, abaturage ba Koreya y'Epfo bagize imyumvire itandukanye bitewe n'uko Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyakiriye.
Abaturage benshi bo muri Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko yamaganaga Moon kubera ibyo babona ko ari ubusumbane mu miyoborere ya leta mu gucunga icyorezo, mu gihe abandi bashyize umukono ku nyandiko ishimagiza uko yitwaye.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite umubare muto w'abanduye ku munsi mu byumweru bine bishize.
Ku ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku ya 1 Mata, abantu bose bavuye hanze bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Amakuru atangwa n'ibitangazamakuru yo ku ya 1 Mata avuga ko Koreya y'Epfo yahawe ubufasha bw'ibihugu 121 mu gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ko abantu ba mbere banduye SARS-CoV-2 kuri 19 Gashyantare i Qom, aho abantu babiri bapfuye kuri uwo munsi nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi yabitangaje.
Ingamba za mbere zatangajwe na leta zirimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, amarushanwa ya siporo n'amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, ndetse no guhagarika kaminuza, amashuri makuru n'amashuri.
Iran yatanze miliyari 5 z'amanyarwanda mu kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani ku ya 26 Gashyantare 2020 yavuze ko nta gahunda yo gushyira mu kato uturere twanduye virusi, ko abantu bonyine ari bo bagomba gushyirwa mu kato.
Gahunda yo kugabanya ingendo zo hanze y'umujyi zatangajwe muri Werurwe, ariko urujya n'uruza rwinshi hagati y'imijyi y'igihugu rwakomeje mbere y'umwaka mushya wa Irani.
Ingoro yera y'aba Shiite mu mujyi wa Qom yari ifunguye ku bayoboke kugeza ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020.
Hagati y'ibyifuzo byo guhisha ko iki cyorezo cyateye muri Irani, ibihugu birenga icumi byatangaje ko iki cyorezo cyateye muri Iran kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare, bikaba bigaragaza ko iki cyorezo gishobora kuba gikomeye kurusha ibindi 388 leta ya Iran yari imaze gutangaza kugeza icyo gihe.
Inteko ishinga amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, maze abantu 23 mu bantu 290 bayigize batangaza ko basanze virusi ya coronavirus ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku ya 12 Werurwe, Umugenzuzi w'Uburenganzira bwa Muntu yasabye abayobozi ba gereza muri Irani kurekura nta ntego abaharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira gutandukana mu mahoro, ndetse no kurekura by'agateganyo imfungwa zose zifite uburenganzira.
Bivugwa ko mu duce twugarijwe n'ibiza nk'ibigo by'ifungurwa kandi tudafite ubuvuzi bukwiye, bishobora kuba byoroshye ko virusi ikwirakwira.
Ku ya 15 Werurwe, leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, umubare munini w'abamaze gupfa muri icyo gihugu kuva icyorezo cyatangira.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, nibura abanyapolitiki 12 n'abayobozi ba leta bariho cyangwa bariho barapfuye.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, Iran yari ifite ubwandu bushya bwa coronavirus bushya 50 n'urupfu rumwe buri saha.
Umukozi wa OMS yavuze ko umubare w'abanduye ushobora kuba wikubye inshuro eshanu uwo muri Irani.
Hari kandi abavuga ko ibihano bya Amerika kuri Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku bushobozi bw'icyo gihugu bwo kwishyura amafaranga kugira ngo kibashe guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Komiseri Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ku Burenganzira bw'Ikiremwamuntu yasabye ko ibibazo by'ubukungu ku bihugu byugarijwe cyane n'iki cyorezo, harimo na Iran, byagabanywa.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, icyorezo cyemejwe mu Butaliyani, igihe abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa bageragezwaga SARS-CoV-2 i Roma, bagaragaza ko banduye.
Umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye cyane, bituma leta y'Ubutaliyani ihagarika ingendo z'indege zinyura mu Bushinwa no gutangaza ibihe bidasanzwe.
Nyuma yaho, havumbuwe umubare utari uhwanye w'abanduye COVID-19, uhereye ku bantu 16 bemejwe ko banduye muri Lombardy ku ya 21 Gashyantare. Ku ya 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje ko yemeje itegeko rishya rigamije gukumira ikwirakwira ry'iki cyorezo, rikubiyemo gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 mu ntara 11 zitandukanye zo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe, Giuseppe Conte, yavuze ko "mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo, kwinjira no gusohoka bibujijwe".
" Amabwiriza akenewe yo guhagarika ibikorwa by'akazi n'imikino mu duce twamaze gutangwa. ""Ku ya 4 Werurwe, nyuma y'urupfu rw'abantu 100 mu Butaliyani, leta yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza zose mu gihugu hose zifungwa burundu. "
Imikino yose ikomeye, harimo n'imikino ya Serie A, yakinwe inyuma y'inzugi kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe mu gihe cy'ukwezi.
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Kent yategetse ko ibikorwa byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarikwa, uretse amaduka manini n'amaduka y'imiti. Ku ya 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'Ubutaliyani cy'Abaganga b'Abaganga, Abatabifite, Abafasha mu Bwizigame n'Abafasha mu Buvuzi bw'Icyiciro Cyihariye (SIAARTI) cyasohoye inama ku bijyanye n'imyifatire y'abaganga ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza atatu ashobora gukoreshwa.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa mu bihugu bifite umubare munini w'abantu bahitanywe na coronavirus ku isi, aho hari abantu 3,405 bishwe n'icyorezo mu munsi umwe.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko Uburusiya bwohereje indege icyenda z'intambara zirimo ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Kuva ku ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hamaze kuboneka abarwayi 128,948, abantu 15,887 bapfuye n'abakize 21,815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kuba u Butaliyani bufite umubare munini w'abantu barembye no kuba abantu bose banduye virusi batashoboraga gupimwa, bishobora kuba ari byo byatumye hapfa abantu benshi.
Ubwongereza bwabanje kugaragaza ko nta ruhare rugaragara bwagize muri icyo cyorezo, kandi kugeza ku ya 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyari yarashyizeho uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda abantu cyangwa gushyira abantu mu kato.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko leta yanenzwe kubera ko ititaye ku buryo bwihuse kandi bufatika bwo gusubiza ibibazo by'abaturage. Ku ya 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson mu ijambo rye yabujije ingendo zitari ngombwa no kwifatanya n'abandi, asaba abantu gukora mu rugo igihe bishoboka, no kwirinda kujya ahantu nko mu tubari, muri resitora no muri sinema.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro, nk'aho ari utubari n'amazu y'imikino, bigomba gufungwa vuba na bwangu, kandi ko izatanga 80% by'umushahara w'abakozi kugeza ku giciro cya A$2,500 ku kwezi, mu rwego rwo kwirinda ko ubushomeri bwiyongera muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ko ingamba zo kwirinda abantu mu buryo bukomeye kurushaho zizashyirwa mu bikorwa, ko abantu barenze babiri batagomba guteranira hamwe, kandi ko ingendo n'ibikorwa byo hanze bizagerwaho mu rugero rukenewe.
Mu buryo bunyuranye n'uko byari bimeze mbere, izo ngamba zashyizweho n'igipolisi, zitanga amande n'uburyo bwo gusenya abaturage.
"Ubucuruzi bwinshi bwarahagaritswe, uretse gusa ubucuruzi bwabonwaga ko ari ""bukenewe"", harimo amaduka manini, farumasi, banki, amaduka acuruza ibikoresho, aho bakorera lisansi n'aho bakorera imodoka".
Ku ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wanduye COVID-19 yamenyekanye mu ntara ya Washington iri mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika, mu gihe yari avuye i Wuhan ku ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abakozi ba White House kuri coronavirus ryatangiye gukora ku ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko ubuzima bw'abaturage buri mu bihe bidasanzwe, bwubahiriza amategeko abuzanya abagenzi bava mu Bushinwa.
Ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ikigo cy'ubuzima rusange cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyateguye ibikoresho byacyo byo gupima.
Nubwo Amerika yabigenje ityo, yatangiye gupima vuba, bituma umubare nyawo w'icyorezo udasobanuka.
Ibizamini byakozwe mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (bisaba imiti y'abaganga) byafashwe nk'ibidakwiriye kubera ibikoresho by'ibizamini by'ibyangiritse byakozwe na leta muri Gashyantare, kubera ko ibikoresho by'ibizamini by'abikorera bitemewe na leta (binyuze mu nzego z'ubuvuzi, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) bitarangiye muri Gashyantare, n'ibipimo bigabanya abantu bujuje ibisabwa kugira ngo bapimwe.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru Washington Post cyatangaje ko ibizamini byagiye bikorwa muri Amerika ari munsi ya 4000.
Kugeza ku ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyatangaje ko hari hasigaye ibipimo 14,000.
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko abantu benshi bagaragaje ibimenyetso kandi bagasaba abaganga kubapima, bategereje amasaha menshi kugeza ku minsi kugira ngo bapimwe. Nyuma y'ibyabaye ku wa 29 Gashyantare, ubwo hapfaga abantu ba mbere muri Amerika, guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko igihugu kiri mu bihe bidasanzwe, igikorwa cyahise gikurikirwa n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yafunze amashuri ku ya 3 Werurwe, kandi hagati muri Werurwe, amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yafunzwe. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga mu by'indwara zo mu bwoko bwa Epidemiologists bo muri Royal College i Londres batanze imibare y'ingaruka za coronavirus muri Amerika.
Kuri uwo munsi, Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'inguzanyo y'inkunga y'inyongera yo guhangana n'icyorezo, ryatanze miliyari 8.3 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira ibikorwa by'inzego za leta mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Amashyirahamwe yashyizeho amategeko abuza abakozi gukora ingendo, yahagaritse inama kandi atera abakozi inkunga yo gukorera mu rugo.
Ibikorwa n'ibihe by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Trump yashyizeho amategeko yo guhagarika ingendo mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, usibye Ubwongereza, mu gihe cy'iminsi 30, kuva ku ya 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yashyizeho amategeko agenga Ubwongereza na Ireland.
Ku ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje ibihe bidasanzwe ku rwego rw'igihugu, bituma amafaranga ya leta ashyirwa mu bikorwa mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Guhera ku ya 15 Werurwe, ubucuruzi bwinshi muri Amerika bwafunze cyangwa bugabanya amasaha y'akazi mu rwego rwo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Kugeza ku ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu bihugu 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku ya 23 Werurwe, umujyi wa New York wavuze ko abantu 10,700 banduye coronavirus, baruta umubare w'abanduye bose muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku ya 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko kwirinda abantu bigaragara ko ari ingirakamaro, kuko imibare y'uko umubare w'abanduye wiyongereye kabiri yavuye ku minsi ibiri igera ku minsi 4,7.
Kugeza ku ya 28 Werurwe, muri New York City hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 32308 banduye coronavirus, naho abantu 672 bapfuye bayanduye. Ku ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yatangaje ko ifite umubare munini w'abanduye coronavirus kurusha ikindi gihugu icyo ari cyo cyose ku isi, harimo n'u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Kugeza ku ya 8 Mata, hari hamaze kugaragara abantu 400335 banduye coronavirus muri Amerika, naho abantu 12841 bapfuye.
Nk'uko bitangazwa n'ibitangazamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida Trump wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bwa USNS Comfort bwari bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000 bwafashe ubwato bw'i New York.
Ku ya 3 Mata, Amerika yatsinze umubare munini w'abantu 884 bishwe na coronavirus mu gihe cy'amasaha 24.
Ku ya 3 Mata, abantu barenga 100.000 baranduye muri leta ya New York. Ibiro bya White House byanenzwe kubera kwirengagiza ibyihebe no kugabanya amabwiriza y'abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu guhuza itangazo rusange n'ibyatangajwe na perezida wungirije Mike Pence.
Kwishimira cyane uburyo Trump yafashe iki kibazo mu mashyaka, byaragabanutse.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika banenze ko bishingikiriza ku bicuruzwa by'ibanze biva mu Bushinwa, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryakozwe mu rwego rwo kureba no guhanura uburyo virusi ikwirakwira, risohoka mu kinyamakuru cyitwa Travel Medicine mu kwezi kwa mbere hagati kwa 2020.
Dukurikije amakuru yo mu 2018 yatanzwe n'ishyirahamwe mpuzamahanga ry'ingendo z'indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo bihugu byafashe ingendo nyinshi z'abagenzi bava i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne ni byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu hakunzwe cyane n'abagenzi baturutse mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
Bali ni yo yabaye iya mbere mu mijyi 20 ikunzwe cyane mu kwirinda, mu gihe Australia ari yo yari yiteguye cyane. Australia yatangaje gahunda y'ubutabazi bw'ibiza bya Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku ya 7 Gashyantare.
Iryo tangazo ryagaragaje ko amakuru menshi ku cyorezo cya COVID-19 ataraboneka, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu kugenzura imipaka no guhanahana amakuru mu guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ko habaye ikibazo cy'ubukene mu rwego rwo kurinda ikiremwamuntu.
Kubera guhagarika ingendo rusange mu mujyi wa Wuhan na Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateguye gucyura abaturage n'abakozi ba dipolomasi muri ako karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ndege z'ingendo z'indege ziturutse mu gihugu cy'ibanze, zemejwe n'abategetsi b'Ubushinwa.
Canada, Amerika, Argentine, Ubudage na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byashyizeho gahunda yo gucyura abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yavuze ko nta muturage wayo izasubiza mu gihugu.
Ku ya 7 Gashyantare, Bresil yirukanye abaturage 34 b'igihugu cya Bresil cyangwa abagize imiryango yabo, hamwe n'abanyapolonye bane, Umushina umwe n'Umuhinde umwe.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'Ubuhinde bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye, aho indege ya Bresil yari igeze mbere yo gukomeza urugendo iherereye muri Bresil.
Abaturage ba Burezili bari bagiye i Wuhan bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasilia.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abanyakanada 215 (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere na 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari ikodeshejwe na Leta ya Amerika) bakuwe i Wuhan bajya muri CFB Trenton, aho bari kumara ibyumweru bibiri mu kato.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye abantu 185 b'Abanyakanada ivuye i Wuhan yaguye muri CFB ya Trenton.
Abategetsi ba Autriche bajyanye abaturage 277 ku itariki ya 3 na 4 Gashyantare mu kigo cya Christmas Island, cyahindutse ahantu ho kwicumbikira, aho bamaze iminsi 14.
Indege y'i New Zealand yageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare; abagenzi bayo (harimo n'abaturutse muri Australia na Pasifika) bakuwe ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Whangaparawa mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zigiye gukura Abanyamerika ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku ya 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 b'Abanyakanada bari bakuwe mu bwato bw'akazi bwa Diamond Princess, yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, guverinoma y'u Buhinde yafashe ingamba zo gucyura abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku ya 14 Werurwe, indege y'indege ya Afurika y'Epfo yasubije muri iki gihugu abaturage 122.
Abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus, bakomeje kugenzurwa mbere yo gutangira urugendo kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abantu bo muri Afurika y'Epfo gusa bagaragaje ko nta bimenyetso byafashwe, ni bo basubijwe mu gihugu.
Ibipimo byafashwe n'abaturage bose ba Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi bo mu ndege, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu butumwa bw'ubutabazi, bashyizwe mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 mu rwego rwo kwirinda, mu kigo cya Ranch Resort.
Ku ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yakuye igice cy'ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera icyorezo.
Ku ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byoherereje u Bushinwa inkunga.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri kaminuza zo muri Amerika bifatanyije mu gufasha kohereza imfashanyo mu bice by'u Bushinwa byibasiwe na coronavirus. Itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa mu karere ka Chicago ryatangaje ko ryashoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku ya 30 Mutarama. Ishami ry'ubutabazi ryitwa Direct Relief, rifatanyije na FedEx, ryatumye udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwisungane mu kwivuza birimo utwenda two mu ntoki n'udupfukamunwa, ku ya 30 Mutarama, binyuze mu ndege y'ubutabazi bwihutirwa ku bitaro bya Union Hospital i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje inkunga ya miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ya Amerika ku Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku rukingo n'uburyo bwo kurukiza no gufasha "abantu bafite ibyago byinshi muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Amajyepfo".
Interaksiyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 20 000 muri Filipine ku ya 6 Gashyantare, nyuma yaho Senateri Richard Gordon yoherereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku ya 19 Gashyantare, Croix Rouge ya Singapour yatangaje ko igiye kohereza inkunga y'amadolari ya Amerika miliyoni 2.26 mu Bushinwa.
Ubuyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni muri Wuhan, Turukiya yohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, Uburusiya bwohereje toni zirenga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi muri Wuhan, Malaysia yatangaje ko yatanze toni 18 z'amaboko y'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, Ubudage bwohereje toni zirenga 10 000 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birimo imyenda yihariye, Amerika yohereje toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa, ndetse n'amafaranga ya miliyoni 100 y'amadolari yo gufasha ibihugu byanduye.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'impuguke mu Butaliyani kugira ngo zifashe guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umucuruzi w'icyamamare Jack Ma yoherereje Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia ibikoresho byo gupima miliyoni 1.1, udupfukamunwa miliyoni 6 n'udupfukamunwa 60,000 byo kwambara bikingira umubiri (protective clothing) kugira ngo bikwirakwizwe n'Umuryango wa Afurika Yunze Ubumwe.
Yakomeje yohereza muri Panama ibikoresho byo gupima 5,000, udupfukamunwa 100,000 na ventilators 5.
"Twahawe ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi na Canada. Ubuholandi, Espagne, Turukiya, Georgia na Repubulika ya Tchèque byatangaje ko bitewe impungenge n'udupfukamunwa n'udupfunyika two gupima twakozwe mu Bushinwa".
Urugero, Espagne yahagaritse gukoresha ibikoresho byo gupima byakozwe mu Bushinwa bifite ubuziranenge bwa 30%, mu gihe Ubuholandi bwo bwashyize ahagaragara udupfukamunwa 600,000 tw'ibinyabiziga tw'abashinwa dufite inenge.
U Bubiligi bwanze kwakira udupfukamunwa 100,000 tudakoreshwa, kubera ko bitekerezwaga ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Colombia.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yongeye gutangwa mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Amajyepfo na Afurika. Kuva ku ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubufasha bw'ibihe bidasanzwe ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) rishimye cyane ku mbaraga z'abategetsi b'u Bushinwa mu kurwanya iki cyorezo.
" Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryagereranyije ibi n'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004 aho abayobozi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwaga kudahishira amakuru, bigira ingaruka mbi ku bikorwa byo kwirinda no kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi, kandi mu gihe cy'icyorezo kiriho, guverinoma nkuru ""yashyizeho gahunda yo gutanga amakuru mbere y'ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya w'izuba mu rwego rwo kwirinda icyorezo cy'indwara"."
Ku ya 23 Mutarama, uhagarariye OMS, Goden Gally, yagize icyo avuga ku cyemezo cy'abategetsi bo hagati cyo gushyiraho itegeko ryo kubuza abantu gutembera mu mujyi wa Wuhan, avuga ko "ibi byanze bikunze bitari inama z'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima" ariko ko "byagaragaye ko ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyo kwiyemeza kugabanya icyorezo aho cyagwiriye cyane" kandi ko "bitigeze bibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko hari ubwandu bw'abantu hanze y'Ubushinwa no kwiyongera kw'ibyago mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari ikibazo cy'ubukene bw'ubuzima rusange ku rwego mpuzamahanga, kandi ko ari ubwa gatandatu kibonetse kuva icyorezo cya mbere cy'ibicurane cyatangira mu 2009.
Tedros Adhanom, Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa OMS, yavuze ko PHEIC "ibanze cyane mu bihugu bifite ubukungu buciriritse n'ubukene kandi bidafite uburyo bwiza bwo kwivuza".
Mu gusubiza ku mabwiriza yo kugabanya ingendo, Tedros yatangaje ko: "Nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zitari ngombwa zibuza ingendo n'ubucuruzi ku isi"" kandi akomeza ati ""WHO ntiyifuza ko ingendo n'ingendo bigabanywa".
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Umuryango w'Abibumbye wasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga inkunga ya miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gufasha mu gutanga inkunga y'amafaranga yo gutegura mu buryo bwa politiki mu bihugu bifite amikoro make, wemeza ko ari ngombwa gufasha ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bukwiye bwo gutahura abantu banduye virusi cyangwa bafite ibimenyetso".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "" dukomeye nk'aho tudafite aho duhuriye n'abandi"" asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "gushora imari uyu munsi cyangwa kwikuba kabiri nyuma". Ku ya 11 Gashyantare, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari COVID-19 mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yatangaje ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Loni, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gukoresha "imbaraga z'inyongera z'urwego rwa Loni mu guhangana n'icyorezo".
" Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko itsinda rya ONU rishinzwe kurwanya ibibazo ryinjiye mu bikorwa kugira ngo rihuze ibisubizo byose bya ONU, kandi nk'uko byatangajwe n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, rizemererwa "" kwibanda ku bisubizo by'ubuvuzi, mu gihe izindi nzego zishobora gushyira mu bikorwa ubumenyi bwazo ku bintu byinshi by'imibereho, ubukungu n'ingaruka z'iterambere ry'icyorezo. """
Ku ya 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'umurimo riyobowe na OMS ryashyizwe mu bikorwa kugira ngo ritange impamyabumenyi mpuzamahanga n'ibimenyetso by'ubushakashatsi ku Bushinwa, kugira ngo rifashe mu gucunga no gusuzuma "uburemere n'ubukana bw'iki cyorezo" binyuze mu gukora amahugurwa n'inama n'ibigo by'igihugu no gukora ingendo zo ku butaka kugira ngo harebwe "ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo gusubiza ku rwego rw'intara, intara/intara, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku ya 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "isi ikeneye gukora byinshi mu kwitegura icyorezo cya coronavirus", ivuga ko nubwo hakiri kare cyane ko cyitwa icyorezo, ibihugu bigomba "kwitegura".
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo kiri kwiyongera muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda rya misiyo ihuriweho mu gihugu cyo muri Irani kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko icyiciro cy'ibyago bya Coronavirus ku isi kizamuka kikava ku "kizamutse" kikajya ku "kizamutse cyane".
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru wa gahunda y'ibihe bidasanzwe ya OMS, mu itangazo yatanze, yaburiye ati ""Ibi ni ukuri ku butegetsi bwose bw'isi: haguruka".
" Virusi iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kwitegura, wibuke ko igisubizo cyiza gishobora gufasha isi kwirinda ""gukomeza kuba bibi""".
Ryan yakomeje avuga ko amakuru ariho ubu adashobora kwemeza ko inzego z'ubuzima zemeza ko iki cyorezo ari icyorezo ku isi kuko ibyo bivuze ko "tuzi neza ko umuntu wese ku isi ashobora kwandura iyi virusi".
Ku ya 11 Werurwe, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryatangaje ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus ari icyorezo ku isi.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko "ihangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo biteye impungenge by'ubwandu n'uburemere bw'indwara hamwe n'ibipimo biteye impungenge by'uburangare".
Mu bitekerezo bya politiki byatanzwe harimo n'icyifuzo cy'umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS, Tedros Adhanom cyo kwegura, cyashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 guhera ku ya 6 Mata.
Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu zasabye ko uburenganzira bw'abantu bwubahirizwa mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko ingamba zo kurokora ubuzima zigomba gushyirwa mu bikorwa na buri wese kandi ko ari inshingano za leta.
Iri tsinda ryashimangiye ko kuba umuntu adafite amafaranga cyangwa adafite ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagomba kuba impamvu yo kubarwanya.
Aba bahanga bemeje ko buri muntu wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, abantu bafite ubumuga, abafite ubumuga, impunzi z'abasangwabutaka, abatagira aho baba, ababana n'imimerere mibi, abafunzwe, impunzi n'abandi bakeneye ubufasha bwa leta.
Ibigo bya leta mpuzamahanga birimo gucunga ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho y'abaturage z'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Ubumwe n'Ubutwererane mu by'Ubukungu n'Iterambere ryatangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru ku gihe kandi arambuye ajyanye na politiki y'ibisubizo mu bihugu byo ku isi, hamwe n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku ngamba zo gukomeza ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku gusuzuma ingaruka z'igenzurwa ry'ingendo n'ibihano byo guhagarika ingendo, Digital Hub ikubiyemo gukurikirana politiki y'igihugu (uburyo ibihugu byitabira iki cyorezo) kandi igamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga ku byiboneye kandi byorohereza igisubizo cy'isi yose ku kibazo cya coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenzwe na Minisitiri w'abaminisitiri w'Amerika, Michael Gove n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Burezili, Jair Bolsonaro, ku buryo yahagaritse icyorezo cyatangiriye mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Abategetsi benshi bo mu Bushinwa (CPC) birukanywe mu kazi kubera ubuyobozi bwabo mu rwego rwo gushyiraho gahunda yo gushyira mu kato mu Bushinwa rwagati, bigaragaza ko badashimishijwe n'uburyo inzego za politiki zitabiriye iki cyorezo muri utwo turere.
Bamwe mu banenga ibi bitekerezo bavuga ko icyo gikorwa cyari kigamije kurinda Xi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ry'Ubushinwa, uburakari bw'abaturage bamugiriye muri iki gihe cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi bakuru b'Ubushinwa, nka Zhao Lijiang, banze ko abantu bamenya mbere y'igihe ko Wuhan yarwaye coronavirus, bituma Amerika n'u Butaliyani bibaza niba ari bo bateje icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ubutegetsi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika bwise coronavirus "Virus y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "Virus ya Wuhan" buvuga ko "bwatumye habaho ivangura ry'ubwoko bwa virusi ubu ryahindutse icyorezo ku isi", ibyo bikaba byarakomwe mu nkokora n'abamunenga bamwe bavuga ko ari amacakubiri ashingiye ku moko kandi "binyomoza intege nke z'ubutegetsi bwe mu kurwanya iki cyorezo".
Daily Beast yahawe umurongo wa cable wo gutangaza amakuru n'inama y'umutekano w'igihugu ikoresha ingamba ziswe "byose biri munsi y'umutwe w'Ubushinwa".
"Turasabwa gukora ibishoboka byose kugira ngo tugaragaze ubutumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama z'abanyamakuru n'ibiganiro kuri televiziyo. ""Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Foreign Policy na Bloomberg byatangaje ko imbaraga z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byazahajwe na virusi ari kimwe mu bikorwa by'ubushakashatsi bw'icyo gihugu mu rwego rwo kugira ingaruka ku isi".
Joseph Burrell, ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga y'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'Uburayi, yaburiye ko "hari igice cya politiki y'isi kirimo kugerageza kugira ingaruka binyuze mu kwiyoberanya no 'gushyiraho politiki y'ubuntu.'"
Burrell yakomeje avuga ko "Ubushinwa bushishikajwe cyane no kwereka abantu bose ko bushyigikiye kandi bwizeye ubufatanye n'Amerika".
Ubushinwa bwongeye gusaba Amerika gukuraho ibihano ku gihugu cya Syria, Venezuela na Iran kugira ngo ibafashe, kandi kugeza ubu bwatanze imfashanyo nyinshi muri ibyo bihugu bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, ibihano bya Amerika byabujije Jack Ma guha Cuba udupfukamunwa 100,000.
Abategetsi ba Amerika kandi bashinjwa ko batanze imfashanyo z'ibindi bihugu.
Hari ibindi bihugu byatangaje ko bitumvikana ku bijyanye n'imisatsi, urugero nk'u Budage, Autriche n'u Busuwisi, Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Byongeye kandi, Turukiya yafashe imodoka amagana z'imashini zitanga umwuka zigana muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro za Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yanenze cyane EU kubera ko itafatanyije n'u Butaliyani bwatewe na coronavirus.
Maurizio Massari, ambasaderi w'Ubutaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko Ubushinwa ari bwo bwonyine bwagize icyo bukora.
"Mu by'ukuri, ibi si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubumwe bw'Uburayi""
Ku ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo kuvugana kuri telefoni na Minisitiri w'Intebe w'Ubutaliyani, Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya, Vladimir Putin, yohereje ingabo z'Uburusiya mu Butaliyani kohereza imiti ya gisirikare, ibikoresho byihariye byo kurwanya indwara n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru cyo mu Butaliyani cyitwa La Stampa, cyatangaje ko 80% by'imfashanyo u Burusiya bwahaga Ubutaliyani "nta cyo imaze cyangwa nta cyo imaze", bivuye ku "soko ya politiki ikomeye" itazwi.
"Urubuga rwashegeshwe n'Uburusiya rwamushinje gukoresha nabi "imiterere ya "geopolitique na diplomatique" binyuze mu bikorwa bye by'uburiganya".
Attilio Fontana, umuyobozi wa Lombardy na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga w'Ubutaliyani, Luigi Di Maio, bahakanye amakuru y'itangazamakuru kandi bashimira imihati.
Uburusiya bwohereje indege itwara ubufasha bw'ubuvuzi muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin, Dmitry Peskov yagize ati "" Igihe twatangaga ubufasha ku bakoranabikorwa bacu muri Amerika, twatekerezaga ko igihe abacuruzi b'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'ibikoresho muri Amerika bari kuba batangiye imirimo yabo, na bo bari kuba bashobora kudufasha mu gihe bibaye ngombwa. """
" Imyitozo ya NATO iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye n'ibihugu bya Baltique, "Defender 2020", ni imyitozo ikomeye cyane kuva intambara y'ubutita yarangira, izaba ku kigero cyagabanutse".
Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa Kaminuza ya Iran, Kate Hudson, yanenze imikorere ya Defender 2020 agira ati: "Mu bibazo by'ubuzima rusange biriho, ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'i Burayi biri mu kaga, ariko n'ubw'abaturage bo mu bihugu bikoreramo ibikorwa by'intambara".
Perezida wa Iran, Hassan Rouhani, yoherereje abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa ifunguye ku ya 14 Werurwe 2020, asaba ubufasha avuga ko igihugu cye kiri mu bikorwa byo kurwanya icyorezo cy'iyi ndwara kubera kutagira amahirwe yo kugera ku masoko mpuzamahanga bitewe n'ibihano bya Amerika kuri Iran. Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika ishyiraho politiki z'imibereho myiza nk'uko bikorwa mu bindi bihugu bikize, harimo ubuzima rusange, kwita ku bana bose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango n'amafaranga menshi yo gukoresha mu kwivuza.
Abasesengura ibya politiki bavuze ko iki cyorezo gishobora kugira ingaruka mbi ku buryo Donald Trump azongera gutorwa mu matora ya Perezida wa Amerika yo mu 2020 no ku mibanire y'Ubuyapani na Koreya y'Epfo.
" Nyuma y'aho Ubuyapani butangaje ko abagenzi bose bavuye muri Koreya y'Epfo bazajya mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce twateganyijwe na leta, Koreya y'Epfo yanenze Ubuyapani ivuga ko " nta cyo buzi ku mihati y'ikurwa mu kato".
Kuva icyo gihe, abaturage ba Koreya y'Epfo batangiye kugira impungenge z'uburyo Perezida Moon Jae-in yakiriye iki kibazo.
Abantu benshi bo muri Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko zisaba Moon kwegura, cyangwa se bashimira uburyo leta itakoresheje neza mu kurwanya iki cyorezo. Iki cyorezo cyatumye ibihugu byemera amategeko y'ibihe bidasanzwe kugira ngo bigire icyo bikora.
Bamwe mu batanga ibitekerezo bagaragaje impungenge ko ibyo bishobora gutuma leta zigira ububasha bukomeye.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko y'icyo gihugu yatoye ko Minisitiri w'Intebe Viktor Orbán ashobora kuyobora ku gihe kitagira iherezo, ko inteko ishinga amategeko n'amatora bihagarikwa, kandi ko abakwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma ku ndwara n'uburyo leta itegura ibibazo bahanwa.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyatewe n'ibihe byinshi by'ibura ry'ibikoresho, biterwa no kwiyongera kw'ibikoresho byo kurwanya icyorezo, ubwoba bwo kugura no guhungabana mu mikorere y'inganda n'ibikoresho.
Ikigo cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze imiburo ku bijyanye n'ibura ry'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitewe n'ukwiyongera kw'ibyifuzo by'abakiriya n'ibiza mu isoko.
Uturere dutandukanye twongeye kubona abantu benshi cyane bagiye guhaha, bituma amaduka atagira ibicuruzwa by'ibanze nk'ibiribwa, udupfunyika two mu bwiherero n'amazi y'ibyatsi, bituma habaho ubukene.
Ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga cyatanze umuburo ku bijyanye n'ibihe byo gutumiza ibicuruzwa bya elegitoroniki.
Nk'uko byatangajwe na Tedros Adhanom, Umunyamabanga Mukuru wa OMS, ibisabwa ku bikoresho byo kwirinda byiyongereye inshuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro byiyongera inshuro makumyabiri ugereranyije n'ibisanzwe, bituma ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi bidatangazwa mu gihe cy'amezi ane kugeza kuri atandatu.
Ibi kandi byatumye ku isi hose habaho ikibazo cy'ibikoresho byo kwirinda, kandi OMS yaburiye ko bishobora gushyira ubuzima bw'abakozi mu kaga.
Muri Ositaraliya, iki cyorezo cyatumye abacuruzi ba Diego babona uburyo bushya bwo kugurisha ibicuruzwa bya Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye mu maduka manini habaho ikibazo cy'ibura ry'amata y'impinja, bituma leta ya Australia ibuza ayo mata. Nubwo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani hari abantu benshi banduye COVID-19 n'akarere ka Wuhan, kandi hakagaragara ko hakenewe ibiribwa byinshi, nta na kamwe muri utwo duce kabayeho ikibazo gikomeye cyo kubura ibiribwa.
Ingamba z'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya icuruzwa ry'ibikoresho by'ingenzi mu buryo butemewe n'amategeko zagize icyo zigeraho, kandi zirinze ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibiribwa byari byitezwe mu Burayi no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Umusaruro w'ibikomoka ku buhinzi mu turere two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani dutanga umusaruro w'ibikomoka ku buhinzi ntiwagabanutse cyane, ariko ibiciro bishobora kuzamuka nk'uko bivugwa n'abahagarariye ako karere.
Ibigega by'ibiribwa byuzuye ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan byatangiye kubaho by'agateganyo, mu gihe abayobozi bakuru b'Ubushinwa bafunguye ibigega by'inyama z'ingurube kugira ngo barebe ko abaturage bahawe ibiryo bihagije.
Amategeko nk'ayo mu Butaliyani asaba abahinzi b'ibiribwa kubika ibicuruzwa byabo mu gihe bibaye ngombwa.
Ubukungu bw'isi bwumvikaniye mu Bushinwa: Nk'uko bitangazwa n'itangazamakuru ku ya 16 Werurwe, ubukungu bw'Ubushinwa bwahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020, bitewe n'ingamba za leta zo kwirinda icyorezo, ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwahise bugabanukaho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari kimwe mu bihugu by'ibanze bifite ubukungu n'inganda nyinshi, iki cyorezo ni kimwe mu bintu bikomeye bibangamiye ubukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demarais wo mu kigo cy'ubushakashatsi mu by'ubukungu (Economist Information Unit) yavuze ko amasoko azakomeza guhungabana kugeza igihe ibizava mu matora bizamenyekana neza.
Muri Mutarama 2020, bamwe mu bahanga mu by'inganda batangaje ko ingaruka z'icyorezo ku bukungu bw'isi zishobora kuba zikomeye kurusha iz'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Nk'uko impuguke zo muri Kaminuza ya Washington i St. Louis zibitekereza, uruziga rw'ibikoresho ku isi rushobora kuzagira ingaruka ku mafaranga agera kuri miliyari 300 z'amadolari, kandi ingaruka zizakomeza mu myaka ibiri iri imbere.
Raporo y'Umuryango w'Ibihugu Bikora Peteroli (OPEC) ivuga ko ibiciro bya peteroli "bigeze ku gipimo cyo hasi cyane" kubera ko Ubushinwa bwagabanyije ibyo bukenera.
Amasoko y'imari ku isi yose yaguye ku itariki ya 24 Gashyantare kubera ubwiyongere bukomeye bw'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'u Bushinwa.
Ku ya 27 Gashyantare, impungenge z'icyorezo cya Coronavirus zatumye ibipimo by'imigabane bya NASDAQ-100, S&amp;amp;P 500 na Dow Jones Industrial Average bigabanuka ku buryo bitigeze bibaho kuva mu gihe cy'ibibazo by'imari mu 2007, Dow Jones igeze ku manota 1191, bikaba ari byo bya mbere byagabanutse ku munsi umwe.
Ibipimo byose uko ari bitatu byari hejuru ya 10% mu mpera z'icyumweru.
Ku ya 28 Gashyantare, ikigo cy'ishoramari cya GMBH Scope cyemeje ko u Bushinwa bufite indangagaciro mbi.
Ibiciro by'imigabane byongeye kumanuka cyane kubera ubwoba bwa coronavirus, kugabanuka kw'ingenzi cyane guhera ku ya 16 Werurwe.
Abantu benshi batekereza ko ubukungu buzagabanuka.
Umuhanga mu by'ubukungu, Mohamed al-Arian, yashimiye ibihano by'ibihe bidasanzwe bya banki nkuru n'ibihugu.
Banki nkuru zitabiriye vuba ugereranyije n'ibibazo by'imari byo mu 2008.
Kubera amategeko agenga ingendo, gufunga ahantu hahurira abantu benshi nko mu bintu by'ingenzi by'ingenzi, no inama za leta zo kutinjira mu bindi bihugu, inganda z'ubukerarugendo ni zimwe mu zangijwe cyane.
Ingaruka zabaye iz'uko hari kompanyi nyinshi z'indege zataye ingendo kubera ikibazo cy'ubukene, harimo British Airways, China Eastern Airlines na Qantas, mu gihe kompanyi y'indege y'akarere y'Ubwongereza Flybe yasenyutse.
Ibi byagize ingaruka ku bucuruzi bw'amato y'ubukwe ku buryo butari bwigere bubaho mbere.
Ibigo byinshi by'indege n'ibibuga by'indege na byo byafunzwe.
Iki cyorezo cyahuriranye n'igihe cy'ingenzi cy'ingendo, gihuza n'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'Abashinwa.
Leta z'ibihugu n'uturere zahagaritse ibikorwa byinshi nk'ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya, kandi ibigo byigenga byafunze amaduka n'ahandi hantu hakurura ba mukerarugendo nka Disneyland Hong Kong na Disneyland Shanghai.
Ibikorwa byinshi byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'ukwezi n'ibindi bikorwa by'ingenzi by'ingenzi byarahagaritswe kugira ngo abantu batongera guterana, harimo n'umugi wabujijwe i Beijing n'ibitaramo by'amasengero.
Mu ntara 24 muri 31, abayobozi b'intara n'uturere bongereye ikiruhuko cy'umwaka mushya kugeza ku ya 10 Gashyantare, bategeka ko ahantu henshi hakorerwa imirimo hatagomba gufungurwa kuri iyo tariki.
Ibi bice byiganjemo 80% by'umusaruro w'imbere mu gihugu na 90% by'umusaruro wo hanze.
Hong Kong yazamuriye ibikorwa byo guhangana n'icyorezo ku rwego rwo hejuru, itangaza ibihe bidasanzwe, ifunga amashuri kugeza muri Werurwe kandi ihagarika ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya. Uruganda rw'ubucuruzi ku isi hose rwagize ingaruka, amasaha y'akazi agabanuka cyangwa akaruhuka by'agateganyo.
Gusura ibigo by'ubucuruzi byagabanutseho 40% mu Burayi na Amerika y'Epfo.
Ubucuruzi bw'ubucuruzi bwo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati na Amerika ya Ruguru bwagize igihombo kiri hagati ya 50% na 60% by'ubucuruzi.
Ibi kandi byatumye ibicuruzwa byagabanuka cyane muri Werurwe ugereranyije n'uko byari bimeze muri Gashyantare.
Abayobozi b'ibigo by'ubucuruzi bikomeye ku isi bashyizeho ingamba zo kubungabunga ubuzima, bashyiraho ibyuma bifata ubushyuhe mu gihe cyo gupima ubushyuhe bw'abaguzi no guhagarika ibikorwa. Komisiyo y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ishinzwe ubukungu muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo, ivuga ko ubukene bwatewe n'icyorezo buzatuma abantu bari hagati ya miliyoni 14 na 22 baba mu bukene bukabije muri Amerika y'Amajyepfo, barenze umubare w'abantu bariho batagira icyorezo.
Muri Mutarama na Gashyantare 2020, mu gihe icyorezo cyari ku isonga mu mujyi wa Wuhan, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 5 mu Bushinwa batakaje akazi kabo.
Abenshi mu bakozi b'abimukira bagera kuri miliyoni 300 bo mu cyaro mu Bushinwa, bari mu mazu yabo mu ntara za kure cyangwa mu ntara ya Hubei. Muri Werurwe 2020, Abanyamerika barenga miliyoni 10 batakaje akazi kabo basaba ubufasha.
Banki nkuru y'igihugu y'igihembwe cya Saint Louis, ivuga ko icyorezo cya coronavirus gishobora kugira ingaruka ku kazi ka miliyoni 47 muri Amerika, ndetse kigatuma ubushomeri buzamuka bugera kuri 32%. Mu Buhinde, guhagarika akazi mu buryo bw'inyongera byatumye abakozi b'abimukira b'Abahinde bagera kuri miliyoni icumi (bakorera ku mushahara) batakaza akazi. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo Angus Reid Institute bwagaragaje ko 44% by'imiryango yo muri Canada yagize ikibazo cy'ubushomeri. Kuva igihe hashyiriweho guhagarika akazi mu gihugu cya Espagne mu kwezi kwa gatatu hagati kwa 2020, abakozi bagera ku 900.000 batakaje akazi.
Mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, abakozi b'Abafaransa miliyoni 4 basabye amafaranga y'ubushomeri bw'agateganyo, naho abakozi b'Abongereza miliyoni 1 basabye inguzanyo rusange (Universal Credit). Hafi miliyoni imwe n'igice y'ibigo byo mu Budage byashyizeho gahunda z'akazi k'igihe gito ku bakozi bahabwa inkunga na leta zitwa Kurzarbit.
Porogaramu y'indishyi z'akazi k'igihe gito y'u Budage yemejwe n'u Bufaransa n'Ubwongereza.
Urwego rw'ubuhanzi n'umurage w'umuco rwagize ingaruka zikomeye ku mikorere mibi y'icyorezo, bigira ingaruka ku mikorere y'imiryango n'abantu ku giti cyabo, haba ku bakozi no ku bantu ku giti cyabo ku isi.
Amashyirahamwe y'umuco n'ubuhanzi yagerageje gushyigikira ubutumwa bwayo (akenshi hakoreshejwe amafaranga ya Leta) kugirango abaturage bashobore kugera ku mutungo w'umuco, kubungabunga umutekano w'abakozi bayo n'abaturage, no gushyigikira abahanzi aho bishoboka.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, hirya no hino ku isi, mu rugero rutandukanye, amazu ndangamurage, ibitabo, ibigo by'imyidagaduro n'ibindi bigo by'umuco hamwe n'imurikagurisha, ibirori n'imyidagaduro byahagaritswe cyangwa byigijwe inyuma, byari byarahagaritswe igihe kitazwi.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'iki cyorezo, hakozwe ingamba nyinshi zo gutanga serivisi zindi binyuze mu buryo bwa digitale. Ikindi kintu giheruka kandi cyihuta mu kugabanya ubwandu ni uguhagarika ibirori by'idini, ibirori bikomeye bya siporo n'ibindi bikorwa rusange nk'ibirori by'umuziki n'ibitaramo, inama z'ikoranabuhanga n'imurika imideli.
Ikigo cya Vatican cyatangaje ko umuhango wo gusoza icyumweru cya Pasika i Roma, wagombaga kuba mu cyumweru gishize mu gihe cy'icyunamo cya gikristo, na wo wahagaritswe.
Abasenyeri benshi basabye abakristu bageze mu za bukuru kuguma mu ngo aho kujya mu mihango yo ku cyumweru; amadini amwe na amwe yatambutsa imihango ku maradiyo, kuri interineti cyangwa kuri televiziyo, mu gihe andi asaba abantu kujya mu mihango yo gusenga.
Kubera ko Kiliziya Gatolika y'i Roma yafunze insengero zayo zose, nini n'izito, kandi ikibuga cya Mutagatifu Petero kivaho abayoboke b'amadini yiyita aya gikristo, andi madini na yo yahagaritse imirimo yayo kandi igabanya imiterere y'amateraniro rusange mu nsengero, imisigiti, insengero, insengero n'insengero.
Minisiteri y'Ubuzima ya Iran yatangaje ko kubera icyorezo cy'icyorezo, amasengesho yo kuwa gatanu mu duce twanduye yahagaritswe kandi ko ibigo by'idini byakomeje gufungwa, mu gihe Arabiya Sawudite yabujije abaturage bayo gusura ahantu hatagatifu i Mecca na Medina, mu gihe ibuza abagenzi b'abanyamahanga kwinjira.
Iki cyorezo cyateje ihungabana rikomeye mu mikino y'imikino ngororangingo kuva mu ntambara ya kabiri y'isi.
Imikino myinshi ikomeye yahagaritswe cyangwa yasubitswe, harimo UEFA Champions League 2019-2020, Premier League 2019-2020, UEFA Euro 2020, shampiyona ya NBA n'umwaka wa NHL wa 2019-2020.
Iki cyorezo kandi cyahungabanyije gahunda za Olympic zo mu mpeshyi za 2020 zari ziteganyijwe gutangira mu mpera za Nyakanga; Komite Mpuzamahanga ya Olimpiki yatangaje ku ya 24 Werurwe ko iri rushanwa "rizaba ku itariki itari iya 2020 ariko atari nyuma y'impeshyi ya 2021".
Ibi byatumye abakinnyi benshi binjira mu mikino yo kuri interineti, kandi imbuga nyinshi zo gukina urusimbi kuri interineti zagize ukwiyongera kwinshi mu kwinjira. Ubucuruzi bw'imyidagaduro nabwo bwaragize ingaruka, kandi amatsinda menshi yahagaritse cyangwa yahagaritse ingendo z'ibitaramo.
Filime nyinshi zikomeye, harimo n'izari zisanzwe zikorera kuri Broadway, na zo zagiye zihagarika ibitaramo.
" Bamwe mu bahanzi barimo baragerageza uburyo bwo gukomeza gukora no gusangira ibikorwa byabo kuri interineti nk'uburyo bwo gusimbura ibitaramo bisanzwe bya Live, nk'ibitaramo byo guhererekanya imbonankubone cyangwa gukora ""ibitaramo bya interineti"" bishingiye kuri interineti ku bahanzi bagamije gukora, gukwirakwiza no kwamamaza ibikorwa byabo. "
Kuri interineti, abantu benshi bakoresha virusi ya corona mu rwego rwo gutangaza no gusetsa abantu.
Kuva icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyatangira, abantu bo mu Bushinwa n'abo mu bihugu byo mu Burasirazuba bwa Aziya, hamwe n'abo mu bihugu by'i Burayi bifite ubwandu bwinshi, Amerika n'ibindi, bagaragarijwe ivangura rikomeye, urwikekwe rw'abanyamahanga n'ivangura.
Ibibazo by'ubwoba, gushidikanya n'urugomo byagaragariye mu bihugu byinshi by'i Burayi, Aziya y'Iburasirazuba, Amerika ya Ruguru n'akarere ka Aziya na Pasifika.
Raporo zo mu kwezi kwa kabiri (igihe abenshi mu banduye bari bakiri mu Bushinwa) zagaragaje ko hari amatsinda menshi ku isi yari afite amarangamutima y'ivangura rishingiye ku moko, avuga ko abaturage b'u Bushinwa bakwiriye gukingirwa n'icyo cyaha.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe bya Afurika na byo byabonye ko umwuka wo kwamagana Ubushinwa wiyongereye.
Abenshi mu baturage ba Wuhan na Hubei batangaje ko bakorewe ivangura kubera ko bakomoka muri ako karere.
Hari abantu batanze ubufasha kuri interineti no hanze yayo baturutse mu bice byibasiwe na virusi mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'uko iki cyorezo cyateye imbere mu bihugu bifite ubwandu bushya, abaturage bo mu Butaliyani, igihugu cya mbere mu Burayi cyahuye n'ikwirakwira rikomeye rya COVID-19, bashobora gukomeza guhura n'amakenga n'ubwoba bw'abanyamahanga. Abaturage bo mu bihugu birimo Malaysia, Nouvelle-Zélande, Singapuru na Koreya y'Epfo babanje gusinya impapuro zibemerera kwinjira mu gihugu cy'Abashinwa mu rwego rwo guhashya iki cyorezo.
Mu Buyapani, hashtag #ChineseDontComeToJapan (Abashinwa ntibaza mu Buyapani) yakunzwe cyane kuri Twitter.
Abashinwa ndetse n'abandi bantu bo muri Aziya mu Bwongereza no muri Amerika batangaje ko igitero cy'ivangura rishingiye ku moko cyazamutse.
Perezida Donald Trump yanenzwe cyane kubera ko yise coronavirus "Virus y'Ubushinwa", ijambo abavuga ko ryerekana ivangura rishingiye ku moko n'urwango rw'Abashinwa".
Abari mu myigaragambyo muri Ukraine bagabye igitero kuri bisi zari zirimo abaturage ba Ukraine n'abanyamahanga bavuye i Wuhan bajyanwa muri Novi Senzari.
Amakuru avuga ko abanyeshuri bo mu majyaruguru ashyira uburasirazuba bw'u Buhinde buhana imbibi n'u Bushinwa n'abo mu mijyi minini y'u Buhinde bafite ubwoba n'ubwoba kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Dilip Khosh, umuyobozi w'ishyaka Bharatiya Janata mu ntara ya Bengali y'amajyepfo, yavuze ko Abashinwa barimbuye ibidukikije, "ni yo mpamvu Imana yabahaye igihano".
" Ayo magambo yaje kwamagwa kandi ashyirwa ku karubanda na konsula y'Ubushinwa i Calcutta, ashyirwa ku karubanda nk'ikosa. Mu Bushinwa, ivangura ry'abanyamahanga n'ivangura ry'amoko ku baturage batari Abashinwa byagiye byiyongera nyuma y'icyorezo, kandi abanyamahanga bafatwa nk ""ibishingwe by'abanyamahanga"" cyangwa babwirwa ko bagomba kujugunywa mu ""bisanduku by'ibishingwe""".
Ibinyamakuru byinshi bifite ibice by'amafaranga byagiye bibikuraho kugira ngo bijye bitangaza amakuru ajyanye na coronavirus.
Abanditsi benshi b'ubushakashatsi batanze inyandiko z'ubushakashatsi ku byerekeye icyorezo cya virusi ku buntu.
Bamwe mu bahanga bahisemo guhita basangiza ibisubizo byabo kuri seriveri zo gutangira gutangaza nk'ibya bioRxiv.
