Ibizamini byo mu mavuriro byo gupima indwara y'ubuhumekero ya coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19) na virusi SARS-CoV-2 ifitanye isano, bikubiyemo uburyo bubiri, uburyo bwo kumenya niba virusi iriho n'uburyo bwo kumenya niba hari abanduye bakorewe umuti urwanya indwara.
Kuba virusi iri mu bipimo byemejwe na RT-PCR, igaragaza RNA ya coronavirus.
Ni ikizamini cyihariye kandi kigamije gusa gutahura RNA ya virusi ya SARS-CoV-2.
Ikoreshwa mu kwemeza ubwandu bushya cyane cyangwa bukomeje.
Kugaragaza abasirikare b'umubiri (seromologie) bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima indwara no kugenzura abaturage.
Ibizamini by'abasirikare b'umubiri bigaragaza umubare w'abanduye, harimo n'abafite ibimenyetso byoroheje ku buryo bitagomba gutangazwa cyangwa se nta bimenyetso bafite.
Ibipimo by'ukuri by'imfu ziterwa n'iyi ndwara n'urwego rw'ubudahangarwa bw'ubwoko mu baturage bishobora kumenyekana hifashishijwe ibisubizo by'iki kizamini.
Kubera ko ibizamini byari bike, kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari gifite amakuru yizewe ku byorezo bya virusi mu baturage.
Kugeza ku ya 23 Werurwe, nta gihugu na kimwe cyari cyarigeze kigerageza abaturage bacyo barenga 3% kandi hari itandukaniro rinini ku mubare w'ibipimo byakozwe mu bihugu bitandukanye ku isi.
Guhinduka bishobora no kugira ingaruka ku rupfu rw'abantu benshi, mu bihugu bimwe na bimwe bikaba bishobora kuba byarabaye hejuru cyane.
Ikoreshwa ry'ikoranabuhanga rya RT-PCR (rRT-PCR) rishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima ibipimo by'ubuhumekero biboneka mu buryo butandukanye, harimo ibipimo by'umuhogo cyangwa ibipimo by'umwanda.
Ibisubizo by'iki cyorezo akenshi bitangazwa nyuma y'amasaha make cyangwa iminsi ibiri.
Igikorwa cya RT-PCR cyakozwe hakoreshejwe ibipimo by'umuhogo gusa mu cyumweru cya mbere cy'indwara ni cyo cyizere.
Nyuma y'aho, virusi ishobora kugenda mu muhogo, ariko ikomeza kwigwiza mu bihaha.
Ku bantu banduye mu cyumweru cya kabiri, ibipimo bishobora gutorwa mu buryo bwo guhumeka bwo hasi hakoreshejwe catheter cyangwa mu kuvoma.
Imwe mu ngero za mbere za PCR yateguwe na Charité i Berlin muri Mutarama 2020, ikoresha uburyo bwa rRT-PCR (reverse transcription polymerase chain reaction) bwatumye hashyirwaho ibikoresho 250.000 byagiye bitangwa n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS).
Ubwongereza bwakoze ikizamini ku ya 23 Mutarama 2020. Kogenebiotech yo muri Koreya y'Epfo na yo yatangije ikigega cyo gupima SARS-CoV-2 cyo ku rwego rw'ubuvuzi gishingiye kuri PCR cyiswe PowerChek Coronavirus ku ya 28 Mutarama 2020.
" Geno ""E"" iri mu bwoko bwose bwa COVID-19 beta, kandi ikurikirana Geno RdRp iri muri SARS-CoV-2 gusa. Mu Bushinwa, BGI Group ni cyo kigo cya mbere cyabonye uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihuse ikigo cy'igihugu cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi, ku gikoresho cy'ikoranabuhanga cya PCR cyo gutahura SARS-CoV-2. Muri Amerika, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara (CDC) cyo muri Amerika gitanga ikigo cyacyo cyo gupima RT-PCR mu gihe nyacyo cya COVID-19 nshya (2019-nCoV) mu bigo by'ubuvuzi rusange binyuze mu ikoranabuhanga rya International Reagent Resource".
Kimwe mu bipimo bitatu bya jenoside mu mashusho ya kera y'ibikoresho by'ibizamini, ntibyari byarakozwe kubera amakosa mu kimenyetso, bituma ibizamini bya CDC i Atlanta bibangamira, bituma umubare w'ibipimo byageragejwe neza ugabanuka ku kigereranyo cy'ibipimo 100 ku munsi muri Gashyantare 2020.
Kuba ibizamini bikoresha ibice bibiri by'ibanze byemewe ntibyamenyekanye kugeza ku ya 28 Gashyantare 2020, maze laboratwari z'intara n'iz'ibanze zemererwa gutangira ibizamini kuva kuri iyo tariki.
Iki cyemezo cyemejwe n'ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti (FDA) mu gihe cy'ibiza. Laboratwari z'ubucuruzi zo muri Amerika zatangiye kugerageza iki cyemezo mu ntangiriro za Werurwe 2020.
Ku ya 5 Werurwe 2020, LabCorp yatangaje ko ibizamini bya COVID-19 bishingiye kuri RT-PCR bizaba byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gihugu cyose.
Quest Diagnostics nayo yashyizeho ibikoresho byo gupima COVID-19 byatangiye gukoreshwa mu gihugu hose kuva ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe 2020.
Nta gihano cy'igenzurwa cyatangajwe; igiteranyo cy'igenzurwa n'isesengura bigomba gukorwa hakurikijwe ibisabwa na CDC.
Mu Burusiya, ikizamini cya COVID-19 cyakozwe kandi gitangwa n'ikigo cya leta cy'ubushakashatsi mu byerekeye virusi na tekinoroji.
Ku ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, iki kizamini cyanditswe n'ikigo cya leta gishinzwe ubuziranenge n'ubuvuzi. Ku ya 12 Werurwe 2020, byatangajwe ko Mayo Clinic yakoze ikizamini cyo gupima COVID-19. Ku ya 13 Werurwe 2020, Roche Diagnostics yahawe uburenganzira na FDA bwo gukora ikizamini gishobora gukorwa mu masaha 3.5 kandi mu byiciro byinshi, bigatuma imashini imwe ishobora gukora ibizamini bigera ku 4128 mu masaha 24.
Ku ya 19 Werurwe 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatanze uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa (EUA) ku kigo cya Abbott Laboratories kubera igerageza ry'urwego rwa Abbott m2000; mbere y'aho, FDA yari yaratanze uruhushya nk'urwo ku bigo bya Hologic, LabCorp na Thermo Fisher Scientific.
Ku ya 21 Werurwe 2020, Cepheid na yo yahawe uruhushya na FDA rwo gukora igerageza ry'iminota 45.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyemeje ko hakorwa igerageza rikoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kongera isoterme ya nucleic acid aho gukoresha PCR.
Kubera ko bidasaba ko habaho ingengabihe y'ubushyuhe bujya buhindurana, ubu buryo bushobora gutanga ibisubizo byiza mu minota 5 gusa, n'ibisubizo bibi mu minota 13.
Ubu muri Amerika hari ibipimo 18,000, kandi Abbott ifite gahunda yo kongera ibipimo ku gipimo cya 50,000 ku munsi. Kuri ubu iri gukora igerageza muri Tayiwani rikoresha umuti wa monoclonal, ikinyabutabire gihuza neza poroteyine ya nucleocapsid (poroteyine N) ya coronavirus nshya; iyi igerageza yizeye ko rizatanga ibisubizo mu minota 15 kugeza kuri 20 nk'igerageza ryihuse ry'ibicurane.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, isuzuma ry'ibyagiye birakorwa ryagaragaje ko "imashini zo mu gatuza z'amashusho z'amashusho nta gaciro zifite mu gupima indwara mu gihe indwara iri mu bihe bya mbere, mu gihe ibipimo bya CT bishobora kuba byarabonetse mbere y'uko ibimenyetso bitangira".
Mu bintu bisanzwe biranga CT harimo ibipimo by'ibirahuri bya matte bifurizanya impande zombi bifite impande, impande zitari zimwe, kandi zitarimo (pôstériore).
Ubutegetsi bwo munsi y'urukoba (subpleural dominance), buza mu gihe indwara, ubwandu n'imiterere y'uburwayi (crazy paving) bizagenda bihinduka.
Ubushakashatsi bwakorewe i Wuhan, aho icyorezo cy'indwara z'imitekerereze cyatangiriye, bwagereranyije PCR na CT, bwerekana ko CT irushaho kumva neza, nubwo idasanzwe cyane, kandi ko hari byinshi mu bimenyetso by'amashusho byayo bihuza n'ibindi bibazo by'ibihaha n'ibibazo by'ubuhumekero.
Kugeza muri Werurwe 2020, Ikigo cy'Abanyamerika gishinzwe Imikorere y'Imitsi cyatangaje ko "CT itagomba gukoreshwa nk'urupapuro rwa mbere rwo gupima COVID-19 mu gupima indwara".
Igice cy'igisubizo cy'umubiri w'umuntu ku burwayi ni ugukora za 'antibodies' nka IgM na IgG.
Ibi bishobora gukoreshwa mu gupima abantu mu minsi 7 cyangwa irenze nyuma yo kugaragaza ibimenyetso, mu gupima ubudahangarwa no kugenzura abaturage. Ibizamini bishobora gukorwa muri Laboratwari z'ibanze (CLT) cyangwa mu gupima ahantu ho kwitabwaho (PoCT).
Sisitemu zigezweho zifite ubushobozi bwinshi mu ma laboratoire menshi zizashobora gukora ibyo bisobanuro, ariko ubushobozi bwo kuzibona buzaba bushingiye ku gipimo cy'umusaruro kuri buri sisitemu.
Ubusanzwe CLT ikoreshwa mu gusuzuma amaraso y'umuntu umwe, ariko hashobora gukoreshwa ibipimo by'imiti kugira ngo harebwe uko abarwayi b'umubiri bitabira indwara.
Kugira ngo hakorwe ibizamini bya PoCT, amaraso ahanini atangwa binyuze mu gutobora uruhu.
Bitandukanye n'uburyo bwa PCR, ntabwo bisaba ko habaho ibikorwa byo kugabanya mbere yo gupima. Ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti cyatangaje ibigo 29 byamenyesheje ikigo ko byubahirije ibisabwa bityo bikaba byarashoboye gutanga ibizamini byabo by'abanduye.
Kuva ku ya 7 Mata 2020, ikigo kimwe gusa cyemewe na FDA mu gihe cy'ibizamini by'ubutabazi. Mu mpera za Werurwe 2020, ibigo by'ubushakashatsi byitwa Euroimmun Medical Laboratory Diagnostics na Epitope Diagnostics byahawe uruhushya rw'ibihugu by'i Burayi ku bikoresho byabyo by'ubushakashatsi, bishobora gutahura IgG na IgA by'abanduye virusi mu bipimo by'amaraso.
Ubushobozi bwo gupima ni ibipimo amagana ku isaha, bityo bikaba byihuta cyane kuruta uko PCR isanzwe isuzuma RNA ya virusi.
Ubusanzwe, abasirikare b'umubiri bashobora kugaragara nyuma y'iminsi 14 icyorezo gitangiye. Mu ntangiriro za Mata, Ubwongereza bwatangaje ko nta gikoresho na kimwe cy'igerageza cy'abasirikare b'umubiri cyaguzwe cyari gihagije.
Hong Kong yashyizeho gahunda aho abantu bakekwaho uburwayi bashobora kuguma mu rugo, "urwego rw'ubutabazi ruha umurwayi uruziga rw'icyitegererezo", umurwayi akishyira mu cyuma cy'ibipimo, akongera akirungika, nyuma y'igihe runaka akagira ibisubizo by'ibizamini. Ikigo cy'ubuzima cy'igihugu (NHS) mu Bwongereza cyatangaje ko kiri kugerageza gahunda yo gupima abantu bakekwaho uburwayi mu rugo kugira ngo hatagira ibyago byo kwanduza mu nzira ijya kwa muganga cyangwa hakenewe kwanduza ambulansi itwaye umurwayi. Mu bigo by'ubwato by'ubushakashatsi bwa COVID-19 ku bantu bakekwaho uburwayi, umukozi w'ubuzima afata ibipimo akurikije ingamba zikwiye.
Ibigo by'ubushakashatsi by'ubushakashatsi byafashije Koreya y'Epfo gukora imwe mu ngamba zihuse kandi ziganjemo ku isi hose zo gupima. Mu Budage, Ishyirahamwe ry'abaganga b'ubwishingizi mu by'ubuzima ku ya 2 Werurwe ryatangaje ko rifite ubushobozi bwo gupima abagera ku 12.000 ku munsi mu ma ambulansi, ugereranyije n'abasaga 10.700 mu cyumweru gishize.
Iyo muganga aguhaye icyemezo cyo gukora ikizamini, ubwisungane mu kwivuza burakwishyura.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi w'ikigo Robert Koch, Ubudage bufite ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 160.000 mu cyumweru.
Kugeza ku ya 19 Werurwe, serivisi z'igerageza zatangwaga ku mafarashi mu mijyi minini.
Kugeza ku ya 26 Werurwe 2020, umubare w'ibizamini byose byakozwe mu Budage ntiwari uzi neza, kuko hari raporo z'ibisubizo by'ibizamini gusa.
Ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe mu byumba by'ibanze bwagaragaje ko nibura ibipimo 483295 byasuzumwe kugeza mu cyumweru cya 12/2020, harimo n'icyumweru cya 12/2020, maze abantu 33491 (6,9%) basuzumwa SARS-CoV-2 bafite ibimenyetso simusiga. Muri Isiraheli, abashakashatsi bo mu bitaro bya Technion na Rambam bahimbye uburyo bwo gupima ibipimo byafashwe ku barwayi 64 icyarimwe, aho ibipimo byose bifatanya, kandi iyo bibonetse ko bifite ibimenyetso simusiga, ibipimo byose bigasuzumwa. Ikigo cy'ubushakashatsi bw'ubutabazi bw'ubutabazi gifite ubuso bwa metero kare 2000 mu mujyi wa Wuhan cyiswe "Huori-Yuan" (mu Kinyarwanda: 火眼, bisobanura "ijisho ry'umuriro") cyatangijwe na BGI mu kwezi kwa kabiri 2020 aho hashobora gupimwa ibipimo 500 ku munsi.
