" Gukaraba intoki kenshi n'isabuni mu "bihe bikomeye" ku munsi, birinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara nyinshi, urugero nk'indwara y'ibisebe n'icyorezo, zitambukira mu nzira y'umuhogo-umuhogo".
Abantu bashobora kwandura indwara z'ubuhumekero nk'ibicurane cyangwa ibicurane iyo batigeze bakaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku maso, izuru cyangwa umunwa (urugero, mu mazuru).
Hariho ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi byo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ku munsi kugira ngo bagabanye ubwandu bw'indwara: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (kubyimba no gukorora), nyuma yo guhanagura indya z'abana (guhindura amasahani), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere na nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa mu gihe ukora ku nyama, amafi cyangwa amagi.
Niba nta mazi n'isabune bihari, ushobora gukaraba intoki ukoresheje imyuka. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) risaba ko umuntu yoza intoki igihe:
Mbere, mu gihe no nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro.
Mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku murwayi.
Nyuma yo guhindura inda cyangwa gusukura umwana wakoresheje ubwiherero.
Nyuma yo guhumeka, gukorora cyangwa gutera akabariro.
Nyuma yo gukora ku matungo, kuyasiga, no gukora ku myanda yayo.
Ubuzima bwiza bw'ubuvuzi ni ibikorwa by'ubuzima bijyanye n'imikorere y'ubuvuzi.
Gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukoresha imiti cyangwa imiti bishobora gukumira cyangwa kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Intego nyamukuru yo gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ubuvuzi ni ukuzitandukanya n'ibimera byanduza (indwara, virusi cyangwa ibindi bikoko bishobora gutera indwara) n'ibikoresho by'imiti bishobora kwangiza cyangwa kurwara.
Ni ingenzi cyane ku bantu bakora mu by'ibiribwa cyangwa mu buvuzi, ariko ni n'imyitozo ikomeye ku baturage muri rusange.
Gukaraba intoki bifite akamaro kanini, harimo kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'ibicurane, koronavirusi n'izindi ndwara zitandura; kwirinda indwara zitera igifu; no kugabanya ubwandu bw'ubuhumekero.
Kandi bigabanya impfu z'abana babyarira mu ngo.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2013 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bwo gukaraba intoki bwarushijeho kunozwa bushobora gutuma abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu barushaho gukura neza.
Mu bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere, umubare w'abana bapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero n'iseru ushobora kugabanuka hifashishijwe imyitwarire yoroheje nko gukaraba intoki n'isabune.
Ibi bishobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa muri izi ndwara ugera kuri 50%.
Ibipimo by'ubutabazi byimakaza gukaraba intoki bishobora kugabanya igifu ku kigero cya kimwe cya gatatu, bikaba bisa n'ibikoresho by'amazi meza mu turere dukennye.
48% by'ibyago byo kugabanuka kw'ibicurane bishobora guterwa no gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune. Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune ni bwo buryo bwiza kandi buhendutse bwo kwirinda iseseme n'indwara z'ubuhumekero (ARI), kandi ni ikintu gikunze gukorwa mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu baturage ku isi hose.
Pneumonia, ARI ikomeye, ni yo mpamvu ya mbere ihitana abana bari munsi y'imyaka itanu, igahitana abana miliyoni 1.8 buri mwaka.
Kurwara ibicurane n'ibicurane by'ibere ni byo bihitana abana bagera kuri miliyoni 3.5 buri mwaka.
UNICEF ivuga ko guhindurira gukaraba intoki mbere yo kurya no nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero, mu buryo burambye, bishobora kurokora ubuzima bw'abantu benshi kurusha urukingo cyangwa ubundi buryo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kuvura, bikagabanya hafi kimwe cya kabiri cy'abapfa bazize iseseme, kandi bikagabanya kimwe cya kane cy'abapfa bazize indwara z'ubuhumekero zikomeye.
Gukaraba intoki akenshi bikorwa hamwe n'ibindi bikorwa byo guhanagura indwara mu mazi, imiti yica udukoko n'indi gahunda y'ubuzima (WASH).
Gukaraba intoki birinda kandi impetigo, yandura binyuze mu guhura n'umuntu imbonankubone.
Ingaruka mbi zo gukaraba intoki ni uko gukaraba intoki kenshi bishobora gutuma umuntu akomereka vuba bitewe n'uko uruhu rwawe rukonja.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe muri Danemark mu 2012 bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki cyane bishobora gutera ibyuya n'ubushyuhe bw'uruhu, bizwi nka eczema cyangwa amate y'uruhu, kandi bikunze kugaragara cyane mu bakozi b'ubuzima.
Gukaraba intoki cyane ni kimwe mu bimenyetso by'indwara y'ubuhumekero (OCD).
Hariho ibihe bitanu by'ingenzi byo gukaraba intoki n'isabuni ku munsi kugira ngo bagabanye ubwandu bw'indwara: nyuma yo kujya mu bwiherero (kubyimba no gukorora), nyuma yo guhanagura indya z'abana (guhindura amasahani), mbere yo kugaburira umwana, mbere yo kurya, mbere/nyuma yo gutegura amafunguro cyangwa mu gihe ukora ku nyama, amafi cyangwa amagi.
Mu bindi bihe byo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rwo kwirinda ikwirakwira ry'indwara harimo mbere na nyuma yo kuvura igikomere cyangwa igikomere, nyuma yo kwitsamura, gukorora cyangwa gukorora; nyuma yo gukora ku myanda y'amatungo cyangwa gukorana n'amatungo; no nyuma yo gukora ku myanda.
Mu bihugu byinshi, umubare w'abantu bakoresha isabune mu gukaraba intoki ni muto.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2015 ku myenda mu bihugu 54 bwagaragaje ko 38,7% by'abantu biyuhagira isabune. Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2014 bwagaragaje ko Arabiya Sawudite ari yo ifite igipimo cyo hejuru cyo gukaraba intoki ku kigero cya 97%, Amerika ikaba hafi y'icya 77% naho Ubushinwa bukaba bufite igipimo cyo hasi ku kigero cya 23%. Hari uburyo bwinshi bwo guhindura imyitwarire mu gukaraba intoki n'isabuni.
