Gukuraho mikorobe ku ruhu byongerwa no kongeramo isabune cyangwa imiti yo gusukura amazi.
Impamvu nyamukuru ituma isabune n'ibimesa byanduza ni ukugabanya inzitizi zo gusama mu mazi, bigatuma isama risohoka neza.
Amazi yonyine nta cyo amaze mu gusukura uruhu, kuko amavuta na poroteyine ari byo bigize ubutaka bw'ibinyabuzima, bitanyuramo amazi mu buryo bworoshye.
Ariko, gusukura n'amazi meza ahagije bifasha...
Kubera ko isabune ikomeye ishobora kongera gukoreshwa, ishobora kuba irimo za mikorobe nke ugereranyije n'uko yakoreshejwe mbere.
Ubushakashatsi buke bwagaragaje ko kwandura kwa bagiteri biturutse ku isabune zanduye zidashobora kwanduzwa, bwagaragaje ko gutwara bagiteri bitashoboka kuko iyo bakoresheje isabune bihanagura.
CDC ikomeza ivuga ko "isabuni y'amavuta ikoreshwa nta gukorana n'intoki ari yo ikwiye".
Amasabune arwanya za mikorobe yamenyekanye cyane mu guteza imbere ubuzima rusange.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya igaragaza ko gukoresha imiti yica udukoko cyangwa imiti yica udukoko ishobora gutuma habaho ibinyabuzima bidashobora kurwara udukoko mu bidukoko.
Icyakora, amasabune arwanya za mikorobe arimo imiti ikunze gukoreshwa cyane, nka triclosan, ifite urutonde rw'ubwoko bw'ibinyabuzima birwanya iyo mikorobe.
Bityo rero, nubwo imiti igabanya ubukana bw'indwara z'ibicurane idashobora kurandurwa n'amasabune arwanya za mikorobe, ishobora kuba idakora neza nk'uko byavuzwe mbere.
Uretse surfactants n'ibikoresho byo kurinda uruhu, iyi formula igezweho ishobora kuba irimo acides (acide acetic, ascorbic na acide lactique) nk'abagenzuzi ba pH, acide benzoïque ifite ubushobozi bwo kurwanya mikorobe n'ibindi bikoresho byoroshya uruhu (aloe vera, vitamini, menthol, ibimera). Isesengura ryuzuye ryakozwe na Kaminuza ya Oregon, ryerekana ko amasabune asanzwe akora neza nk'amasabune ya mbere ya antibacterial arimo triclosan, mu kwirinda indwara no kwica mikorobe.
Amazi ashyushye akwiriye gukoreshwa mu gukaraba intoki ntabwo ashyushye bihagije ngo yice mikorobe.
Bakteri zikura vuba cyane ku bushyuhe bw'umubiri (37°C).
Ariko, amazi ashyushye y'isabune ni meza cyane kurusha amazi akonje yo kwifashisha isabune mu kurandura udukoko duto duto tw'ibinyabutabire, tugize ubutaka n'udukoko.
Nyamara, bitandukanye n'uko benshi babibona, ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko kunywa amazi ashyushye nta ngaruka bigira ku kugabanya umubare w'abanduye virusi.
Ibiribwa bihumanya intoki cyangwa ibihumanya intoki ni ibikoresho bifite urufatiro rutagira amazi byo gusukura intoki.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibikoresho by'isuku byo mu ntoki bitagira amazi (bimwe mu bikoreshwa cyane mu gusukura intoki bishingiye ku nzoga, imiti yo guhanagura intoki, cyangwa imiti yica udukoko) byatangiye kumenyekana.
Akenshi usanga bishingiye kuri alukoro ya isopropyle cyangwa ethanol, hamwe n'imiti ikomeza nk'i karubomeri (polymère ya acrylic acid) ihinduka umutobe, cyangwa se umusemburo nka glycerine mu mazi, cyangwa se ifu igamije koroshya gukoresha alukoro no kugabanya ingaruka zo kumesa za alukoro.
Kongeramo Hydrogene peroxide yoroheje byongera ibikorwa bya antimicrobial. Ibirinda indwara mu ntoki, harimo nibura 60% na 95% by'inzoga, bifite ubushobozi bwo kwica mikorobe.
Antibacterial z'inzoga zirwanya indwara z'ibicurane, zikuraho za bakteriya, za mikorobe zidakira imiti myinshi (MRSA na VRE), zitera igituntu na virusi nyinshi (harimo HIV, herpes, RSV, rhinovirus, inkingo, ibicurane na hepatite) na fungus.
Ibiyobyabwenge bifite alcohol 70% bihitana bagiteri ziri ku ntoki ku kigero cya 99.97% (kugabanya logarithme ya 3.5, bihwanye no kugabanya 35 decibels) mu masegonda 30 nyuma yo kubikoresha, kandi 99.99% kugeza kuri 99.999% (kugabanya logarithme ya 4-5) bihitana bagiteri ziri ku ntoki mu munota umwe.
Ibiyobyabwenge byanduza intoki bishingiye ku nzoga nta ngaruka bigira nk'ibikomeza virusi zanduza intoki (Norwalk), ari na zo zitera indwara y'uruhu. Ibiyobyabwenge byanduza intoki cyangwa ibiyobyabwenge bishingiye ku nzoga bigomba gukoreshwa ku ruhu, bikanyorohereza neza kandi bikagaragaza intoki zombi.
Uruhande rw'imbere n'inyuma rw'amaboko yombi n'ibice byo hagati n'iby'inyuma by'intoki zose, bisukwaho amasegonda agera kuri 30 kugira ngo amazi, ikirenge cyangwa uruhu bikome.
Inkoryo z'intoki zigomba gukaraba neza mu gihe zisigaye zisigaye mu ntoki. Ikigo cyo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara, kivuga ko gukaraba intoki ari byiza cyane cyane iyo bigaragara ko zanduye, kuruta gukoresha umuti wica udukoko.
Impamvu zituma iyi myenda ikoreshwa cyane ni uko yoroshye gukoresha kandi yica mikorobe vuba; ariko, ntiyagombye gukoreshwa nk'isimbura ryo gukaraba intoki neza, keretse niba isabune n'amazi bihari.
Gukoresha kenshi imiti yica udukoko itetse inzoga bishobora gutuma intoki zuma, keretse hagize uwongeraho umuti wo guhumeka cyangwa uwongeraho umuti wo guhumeka.
Ingaruka zo kumesa inzoga zishobora kugabanuka mu kongera glycerine na/cyangwa ibindi bikoresho byoroshya mu buryo.
Mu igerageza ry'ubuvuzi, imiti yica udukoko ikoreshwa mu kuboko irimo n'ibimonyo, yatumaga umuntu atababara cyane kandi ntahumuke cyane ugereranyije n'amasabune arimo imiti igabanya ubukana.
Indwara y'uruhu iterwa n'ubushyuhe, indwara y'ubushyuhe buturuka ku mukondo cyangwa ibyiyumvo byo kurwara inzoga cyangwa ibindi bintu byongera ku nzoga biboneka mu ma gels y'amaboko y'inzoga, si kenshi.
Kubera ko gukaraba intoki n'amazi n'isabune bidateza dermatite y'imibonano iteye isoni cyane, birakunzwe cyane.
Nubwo bifite ubushobozi bwinshi, ibikoresho bitagira amazi ntibikuraho intungamubiri mu biganza, ahubwo birabihumanya.
Ni yo mpamvu imiti yica udukoko mu ntoki idakora neza nk'amazi n'isabuni mu gukumira indwara kuko indwara zikomeza kuba ku ntoki.
Imiti yica udukoko mu ntoki itarimo inzoga igira ingaruka nziza bitewe n'ibikoresho ikoresha n'uburyo ikoreshwamo, kandi mu mateka, nta cyo imaze nk'imiti irimo inzoga cyangwa za gel z'inzoga.
Mu minsi ishize, imiti ikoresha benzalkonium chloride yagaragaje ko ikomeza kandi ikongera ingufu mu kurwanya mikorobe nyuma yo kuyinywa, bitandukanye n'inzoga, kuko iyo ikoreshejwe kenshi, ishobora kugabanya ingufu kubera ko igira ingaruka ziterwa n'ubushyuhe.
Abantu benshi mu baturage batagira amikoro make ntibashobora kugura isabune, bakoresha ivumbi n'imyotsi.
Ivu cyangwa ivumbi bishobora kugira ingaruka nziza kurusha amazi, ariko bishobora kugira ingaruka nkeya kurusha isabune.
Ikindi kibazo cy'impungenge ni ukwanduza ubutaka cyangwa ivu udukoko duto dushobora gutuma indwara ikwirakwira aho kugabanya ubwandu.
Ifu ni umuti wica udukoko, kimwe n'isabune, kuko iyo uhuye n'amazi, uba urimo umunyu.
