Umunsi mpuzamahanga wo gukaraba intoki ni urundi rugero rw'ubukangurambaga bwo gukangurira abantu guhindura imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF yamenyekanishije gukoresha imvugo yo gukaraba intoki.
