Gutegeka ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19.
Gutegeka ibyago byo mu kazi kuri COVID-19 bivuga gushyira mu bikorwa gahunda z'ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi mu rwego rwo kugenzura ibyago no gukumira icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19).
Gutegeka neza ibyago ku kazi biterwa n'aho ukorera n'inshingano, kandi bigira ingaruka ku gupima ibyago biterwa n'aho ubwandu buturuka, ubukana bw'uburwayi mu baturage n'ibyago by'umukozi wese ushobora kwandura COVID-19.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cy'ubwisungane mu kwivuza muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika (OSHA), aho abakozi bafite ibyago bike cyane, bakorana n'abantu benshi n'abandi bakozi, basabwa gufata ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo gukaraba intoki, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukoresha udupfukamunwa no gukora isuku n'imiti yo guhanagura indwara.
Mu kazi k'ibyago biri hagati harimo n'akagenewe abantu badafite ubwandu bwa COVID-19 cyangwa bakekwaho kuyandura, ariko bashobora kuba bafite ibyago byinshi bitewe no guhura n'abantu cyangwa gukora ingendo mpuzamahanga.
Ibi birimo abakozi bahura n'abaturage mu byumba birimo amashuri, ahantu hari abaturage benshi, ndetse no mu maduka manini.
Mu rwego rwo kurwanya ibyago by'iri tsinda, uretse ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda ubwandu, harimo kongeramo umwuka ukoresheje amavuta meza cyane, kurinda gusinzira no gukoresha ibikoresho byo kwirinda umuntu wahuye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19.
OSHA ivuga ko abakozi b'ubuzima bahura n'abantu bakekwaho COVID-19 ari abakozi bafite ibyago byinshi, cyane cyane iyo bakoresha uburyo bwo gukora 'aerosol' cyangwa bakorora ibipimo byafashwe ku bantu bakekwaho COVID-19.
Mu bintu bikwiye gukoreshwa mu kugenzura akaga ko mu kazi, harimo n'ibikoresho byo mu rwego rwa tekiniki, urugero nk'ibyumba bifite umwuka uhumanya nabi n'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bikwiye akazi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 gishobora kugira ingaruka nyinshi ku kazi.
Abakozi bashobora kutabona aho bakorera bitewe n'uburwayi, kwita ku bandi cyangwa gutinya ko bashobora kurwara.
Imikorere y'ubucuruzi irashobora guhinduka, haba mu bijyanye n'ibicuruzwa bisabwa ndetse no mu buryo bwo kubona ibicuruzwa (nk'ibicuruzwa mu masaha y'ikirenga cyangwa binyuze muri serivisi zo gutanga cyangwa serivisi zo gutwara abantu).
Amaherezo, kohereza ibicuruzwa mu turere tw'isi twatewe na COVID-19 bishobora kuba ikibazo. Gahunda yo kwitegura no gusubiza indwara yandura ishobora gukoreshwa mu kuyobora ingamba z'umutekano.
Imishinga ijyanye n'ibikoresho by'akazi n'imirimo itandukanye, harimo aho umuntu ahurira n'indwara, ibintu by'ibyago mu mibereho y'abaturage n'iwabo, hamwe n'ibyago ku mukozi ku giti cye, harimo uburwayi cyangwa uburwayi bw'igihe kirekire, bifatwa nk'ingingo z'ingenzi.
Iyi gahunda igaragaza kandi uburyo bukwiye bwo kugenzura bukenewe mu kwirinda ibyo byago n'uburyo bwo guhangana n'ibihe bishobora gutera icyorezo.
Gutegura no gusubiza indwara zitandura bishobora gukorwa hakurikijwe amabwiriza y'igihugu cyangwa y'akarere.
Intego zo guhangana n'icyorezo ni ukugabanya ubwandu hagati y'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara indwara ziterwa n'uburwayi, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku bindi bigo mu ikoranabuhanga.
Uburemere bw'iki cyorezo mu baturage, aho ibigo by'ubucuruzi biherereye, bigira ingaruka ku bisubizo.
Urutonde rw'ibinyabiziga ni urwego rukoreshwa cyane mu kubungabunga ubuzima n'umutekano mu kazi, mu gushyira hamwe ibihano by'ibyago hashingiwe ku ngaruka.
Mu gihe hatari uburyo bwo kwirinda COVID-19, uburyo bwo kugenzura bufite ingufu cyane ni ubuhanga, nyuma yaho ni ubugenzuzi bw'ibiro, hanyuma ni ibikoresho byo kurinda umuntu.
Kugenzura ubwubatsi ni ukubuza abakozi guhura n'ibiza bijyanye n'akazi, aho kwishingikiriza ku myitwarire y'umukozi, kandi bishobora kuba umuti uhenze cyane.
Ibigo by'ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu mabwiriza cyangwa mu mikorere y'akazi abakozi bagomba gukurikiza.
Ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi (PPE) bifite ingaruka nke ugereranyije n'ibikorwa by'ubuyobozi n'ubwubatsi, ariko bishobora kwirinda akaga.
Ibikoresho byose bya PPE bigomba gutoranywa hashingiwe ku ngaruka bigira ku bakozi, bikagenerwa uburyo bukwiriye (urugero nk'udupfukamunwa tw'ubuvuzi), bikagenerwa igihe cyose kandi bikakoreshwa buri gihe, bikagenzurwa, bigakorerwa serivisi, bigasimbuzwa, kandi bikugururwa, bikanahumanywa, bikongera bikagenerwa igihe bibaye ngombwa, cyangwa bikirukanwa kugira ngo birinde kwandura.
Nk'uko byatangajwe n'ikigo cy'Amerika gishinzwe ubuzima n'umutekano ku kazi (OSHA), imirimo ifite ibyago bike ni iyo ituma abantu benshi cyangwa abakozi bafatanya imirimo badahura n'ibibazo byinshi.
Ingamba zo kwirinda indwara zigomba gufatwa n'abantu mu kazi hose, harimo gukaraba intoki kenshi, gukangurira abakozi kuguma mu rugo mu gihe barwaye, gukoresha udupfukamunwa two guhumeka, ariko birumvikana ko no kwambara mu gihe bakoroye cyangwa batutse, kubona utwenda two kwifashisha n'ibikapu by'imyanda, kwitegura guhanahana amakuru cyangwa gukora amasaha adafite gahunda mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, gukangurira abakozi gukoresha ibindi bikoresho no kugira gahunda ihoraho yo gusukura no guhanagura udukoko mu kazi.
