ACE2 ni enzymes ifata ku gice cy'inyuma (urwangano rw'ingirabuzimafatizo) mu bihaha, mu mitsi, mu mutima, mu gitsina no mu muhogo.
ACE2 ikora ku mikorere ya enzyme ihindura angiotensin binyuze mu kugabanya ingano ya angiotensin 2 no kongera ingano ya angiotensin 1-7, bituma iba umuti mwiza wo kuvura indwara z'umutima. ACE2 ikomeza gukora nk'aho ingano y'abanduye zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi yinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo.
Ubwoko bwa enzyme mu bantu akenshi bwitwa hACE2.
Igisirikare cy'amaraso cyitwa angiotensin-2 kigizwe na metalonzyme ifite uruvange rw'umwimerere ku mubiri w'umubiri.
Poroteyine ACE2 irimo uruziga rwa M2 peptidase N-terminal na polymerine C-terminal amino acid transport domain.
ACE2 ni ubwoko bw'indimu z'uruhu z'uruhu rumwe, zifite ahantu hazima ha enzyme, ziba ku rwego rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bihaha no mu zindi nkorano.
Uruziga rw'inyuma ya ACE2 ruca mu gice cy'urusobe rw'umubiri n'indi ngirabuzima yitwa Shadas, maze poroteyine yabonetse mu maraso igashyirwa mu maraso, amaherezo ikajya mu maraso.
ACE2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ACE2 ifatanye n'urusobe rw'ingirabuzimafatizo mu bice byinshi by'umubiri, mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu nda ntoya, mu ngirabuzimafatizo zo mu mitsi no mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'ingingo z'uruhu mu ngingo nyinshi.
ACE2 mRNA kandi iboneka mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa cortex, mu gice cy'umubiri cyitwa plancton, mu gice cy'amaboko cyitwa hypothalamus no mu gice cy'ubwonko cyitwa stem.
Inshingano nyamukuru ya ACE2 ni ugukora nk'umuti ugabanya ACE.
Hormone ACE igabanya angiotensin 1 ikayigira angiotensin 2, ikora mu kuvura imitsi y'amaraso.
ACE2 yo yica amino acide karboxyl-terminal (AAS) mu bwoko bwa Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-Phe, ikayihindura H-Asp-Arg-Val-Tyr-Ile-His-Pro-OH, ikayihindura angiotensin ikomeza imitsi (1-7).
ACE2 ishobora gutuma ibindi bice by'umubiri bigabanya ingano y'ibinyabutabire, harimo /des-arg9-brededicin, neurotensin, dinorphine A na ghrelin.
ACE2 kandi itegeka ko utwo turemangingo tw'amino acide SLC6A19 tuva mu gice cy'urwungano rw'amaraso, kandi igira uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartt-Behrens.
ACE2 ni poroteyine ihita mu gice cy'umubiri, ikora nk'aho virusi zimwe na zimwe za coronavirusi zinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo, harimo HCoV-NL63 (virusi ituma SARS) na SARS-CoV-2 (virusi ituma COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, guhuza poroteyine ya S1 ya SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV2 n'akarere ka ACE2 ku rwego rw'ingirabuzimafatizo, bituma habaho endocytosis no kwimura virusi na enzymes mu bice by'ingirabuzimafatizo.
