Amahitamo adahangayikisha cyane ni ugukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugirango umenye aho umukoresha aherereye ku zindi terefone zigendanwa.
Ku ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ku mugaragaro ko bagiye gushyira ubushobozi bwo gushyigikira izi porogaramu zishingiye kuri Bluetooth mu buryo butaziguye kuri Android na iOS.
