Kugeza ku ya 6 Mata 2020, ntabwo hari amakuru arambuye yatanzwe.
Gukurikirana guhamagara kugira ngo ubwirinzi bw'ibanga bubeho ni igitekerezo cyemewe cyateye ubushakashatsi bwinshi guhera nibura mu 2013. Guhera ku ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'abahanga arimo gukora ku bisubizo byemewe byo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite, nk'ikoreshwa rya Bluetooth y'ingufu nke (BLE) mu gufata amakuru y'umukozi hafi y'izindi telefoni zigendanwa.
Ariko, PEPP-PT ni umuhate wo guhuza ibintu, ukaba urimo uburyo bwigenga n'ubw'ibanze, kandi ntabwo ari porotokari imwe. Porotokari zitari zisanzwe zirimo gukurikirana aho uherereye n'ibanga (DP-PPT / DP-3T), umubare w'ibitero by'igihe gito (TCN), umubare w'ibyabaye mu guhamagara (FKA, CEN), porotokari z'ibanga, n'uburyo bwo gukurikirana guhamagara kuri telefoni zigendanwa (PACT), n'ibindi.
