Amasabune n'ibimesa nabyo ni ingirakamaro iyo bikoreshejwe neza: ibicuruzwa by'amasabune birandura kandi bikangiza uruhu rw'uruhu rw'ubwirinzi bwa virusi, kandi bikirinda virusi ku ruhu no ku bindi bice.
Ibindi bikoresho nk'ibya benzalkonium chloride na chloroxidine glucanate (indwara yanduza indwara mu gihe cyo kubagwa) ntibikora cyane. Mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe i Hong Kong, ibipimo by'amahembe byafashwe nyuma y'iminsi ibiri umuntu avuye mu bitaro.
Mu barwayi batanu muri batandatu, uwa mbere yari afite virusi nyinshi cyane, naho uwa gatandatu yari afite virusi nyinshi ku munsi wa kabiri.
SARS-CoV-2 ni virusi nshya ya COVID-19 yandura indwara y'ubuhumekero, yagaragaye bwa mbere mu bantu batatu barwaye mu mahaha n'ibinure i Wuhan, barwaye indwara y'umuvuduko muke w'umwuka mu maraso n'ibibazo byo guhumeka.
Ibintu byose biranga SARS-CoV-2 nshya bigaragara mu bwoko bwa koronavirusi.
