Inkomoko nyayo ntizwi, ariko kugeza mu Ukuboza 2019, ikwirakwira ry'icyorezo ryari ryiyongereye cyane kubera ubwandu bw'abantu.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bantu 41 ba mbere banduye COVID-19 bwasohotse muri Mutarama 2020 mu kinyamakuru The Lancet, bwatangaje itariki y'ibimenyetso bya mbere yo gutangira kugaragara ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019.
Inyandiko z'ibiro bya OMS zivuga ko ibimenyetso bya mbere by'indwara byatangiriye ku itariki ya 8 Ukuboza 2019.
Ubusanzwe, hari ibipimo byinshi bikoreshwa mu kubara umubare w'abapfa.
Iyi mibare igenda itandukana bitewe n'akarere n'igihe, kandi igenda itandukana bitewe n'ubwiyongere bw'ibipimo, ireme ry'ubuvuzi, uburyo bwo kwivuza, igihe cyashize kuva icyorezo cyatangira n'ibintu biranga abaturage, urugero nk'imyaka, igitsina n'ubuzima rusange.
Mu mpera za 2019, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryahaye abantu bapfuye bagaragayeho ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2 kode ya ICD-10 yo kwihutisha indwara ya U07.1, naho abamaze gupfa bagaragayeho ubwandu bwa COVID-19 nta SARS-CoV-2 yemejwe, kode ya U07.2. Ikigereranyo cy'urupfu ku bantu banduye, ni umubare w'abantu bapfuye ugabanijwe n'umubare w'abamaze kwandura mu gihe runaka.
Nk'uko byemejwe na Johns Hopkins University, igipimo cy'urupfu ku isi yose kugeza tariki ya 17 Mata 2020 ni 6.9% (15,3822/2,240191).
Ibipimo bitandukanye bitewe n'akarere. Ibindi bipimo birimo igipimo cy'urupfu (CFR), kigaragaza abantu barwaye kandi bapfuye, n'igipimo cy'ubwandu bw'ubwandu (IFR), kigaragaza igipimo cy'abantu banduye (barwaye cyangwa batarafatwa) bapfuye bazize indwara.
Iyi mibare ntabwo ihagarariye igihe kandi ikurikira abaturage runaka kuva ku cyorezo kugeza ku kiza.
Nubwo abarwayi bose badafite abanduye, kuba hari abanduye bigaragaza umubare w'abanduye.
Mu mujyi muto witwa Castiglione d'Adda, mu Butaliyani, aho icyorezo cyatangiriye, abantu 80 (1.7%) mu baturage 4,600 barapfuye.
Muri Ganglet, virusi yageze mu rubyiruko binyuze mu birori bya Carnival, bituma umubare w'abapfa ugabanuka. Icyakora, abantu bose bapfa bazize COVID-19 bashobora kuba atari ko bimeze.
Byongeye kandi, ubuvuzi bw'Ubudage ntibwigeze buhagarika kwakira no kuvura abarwayi.
Mu Buholandi, abantu bagera kuri 3% bashobora kuba bafite abanduye, nk'uko byemejwe n'abatanga amaraso.
Abantu 69 (0.004% by'abaturage) bapfuye bazize COVID-19.
Ingaruka z'icyorezo n'imfu z'abantu bapfa bitewe nacyo bitandukanye ku bagabo n'abagore.
Imibare y'abagabo bapfa iri hejuru mu bushakashatsi bwakorewe mu Bushinwa no mu Butaliyani.
Ibyago byinshi cyane ku bagabo ni mu myaka yabo ya 50 kandi itandukaniro hagati y'abagabo n'abagore ni ibice 90 gusa.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa ku bagabo ni 8.2% naho ku bagore ni 7.1%.
Impamvu nyamukuru ituma habaho itandukaniro ry'ibitsina ntizwi, ariko ibintu byo mu myitwarire n'ibikomoka ku miterere y'ibinyabuzima bishobora kuba ari byo bitera.
Itandukaniro ry'ubushobozi bw'umubiri bwo kwirinda indwara bitewe n'igitsina, kuba abagore batanywa itabi cyane, n'ubukana bw'indwara z'ibicurane mu bagabo, nk'umuvuduko w'amaraso ukabije mu gihe gito ugereranyije n'abagore, bishobora kugira uruhare mu gutuma abagabo bapfa igihe kirekire.
Mu Burayi, 57% by'abanduye ni abagabo, kandi 72% by'abapfuye bazize COVID-19 ni abagabo.
Guhera muri Mata 2020, leta ya Amerika ntiyakomeje gukurikirana amakuru ajyanye no kwandura COVID-19 binyuze mu mibonano mpuzabitsina.
Ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko indwara zituruka ku mikorobe nka Ebola, SIDA, ibicurane na SARS zigira ingaruka zitandukanye ku bagore n'abagabo.
Abagore ni bo bafite umubare munini w'abakozi b'ubuzima, cyane cyane abaforomo, bafite ibyago byinshi byo kwandura iyi virusi.
