Kubera ubushobozi buke mu miyoboro isanzwe y'itangwa ry'umurimo, inganda zimwe na zimwe zikoresha ikoranabuhanga ziri gukora ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi nk'udupira tw'amazuru cyangwa ibice by'imashini z'umwuka.
Urugero, igihe ibitaro byo mu Butaliyani byasabaga vuba cyane umugozi wo guhumeka kandi abaguzi batabifite, ikigo cy'aho cyatangiye gukora ingufu z'isubiramo cyakoze imigozi 100 mu ijoro rimwe.
Nyuma y'icyorezo cya COVID-19, ibitekerezo by'ubuhendanyi, amakuru atari yo n'amakuru atari yo ku nkomoko, ingano, kwirinda, kuvura n'ibindi bintu by'indwara byatangiye gukwirakwira kuri interineti.
Abantu bashobora gukwirakwiza iyi virusi mu bindi bikoko byinshi.
Ubushakashatsi bwashoboye kubona ibimenyetso byerekana ko virusi ishobora kwiyongera mu ngurube, ibyana by'inkoko n'imbeba, bwarananiwe.
Nta muti cyangwa urukingo rwemewe kuvurwa iyi ndwara.
Ubushakashatsi mpuzamahanga ku rukingo n'imiti ya COVID-19 burimo gukorwa n'inzego za leta, amatsinda y'abahanga n'abashakashatsi bo mu nganda.
"Muri Werurwe, OMS yatangije ""igerageza ry'ubwiyunge"" (SOLIDARITY Trial) ryo gusuzuma ingaruka z'imiti ine ya virusi iriho ifite icyizere cyo kugira ingaruka nziza".
Nta rukingo rw'inzobere ruzwi, ariko inzego zitandukanye ziri gukora cyane ku buryo bwa mbere.
Kubera ko SARS-CoV na SARS-CoV-2 byombi bikoresha ACE2 mu kwinjira mu ngirabuzimafatizo z'abantu, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere kuri SARS-CoV bufite akamaro.
Hari uburyo butatu bwo gukingira bwagiye bugeragezwa.
Mu mizo ya mbere, ubushakashatsi bwari bugamije gukora urukingo rw'indwara y'agakoko gatera SIDA.
Gukoresha virusi nk'iyo, yaba idafite ingufu cyangwa yapfuye, bigamije gutera igisubizo cyihuta cy'umubiri w'umuntu ku cyorezo gishya cya COVID-19.
Uburyo bwa kabiri, ni urukingo rw'inkingo, rugamije gukora urukingo rutuma umubiri ugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya virusi runaka.
Ku bijyanye na virusi ya SARS-CoV-2, ubushakashatsi bwibanze cyane kuri poroteyine ya S-spike ifasha virusi kwiyunga na ACE2 receptor.
Uburyo bwa gatatu ni urukingo rwa nucleic acid (inkingo za RNA cyangwa DNA, uburyo bushya bwo guteza imbere urukingo).
Inkingo z'igerageza muri buri buryo zigomba kugeragezwa ku bushobozi n'ubushobozi. Ku ya 16 Werurwe 2020, icyiciro cya mbere cy'igerageza ry'urukingo rwatangijwe n'abakorerabushake bane i Seattle.
Uru rukingo rugizwe na kode y'ubwoko bw'ubwoko bw'ubwoko butariho ingaruka, yakuwe kuri virusi itera iyo ndwara. Iterambere rishingiye ku rukingo rw'umubiri ryashyizwe imbere nk'ikibazo gishobora kuvuka mu gukora urukingo rwa SARS-COV-2, ariko biracyari impaka.
Kugeza muri Mata 2020, hari ibizamini by'ubuvuzi birenga 300 biri gukorwa.
Kugeza ubu, hari ibizamini birindwi byakozwe ku ndwara ya Malaria, harimo n'ibizamini bine byakozwe kuri hydroxychloroquine cyangwa chloroquine.
Ubushakashatsi bw'imiti mishya ya virusi ikora neza cyane bwakozwe n'Abashinwa, aho mu mpera za Mata, mu bihugu bitandukanye hakozwe igerageza ry'ibice icyenda bya gatatu bya Remdesivir.
Kuva muri Mata 2020, hari igikorwa cy'ubushakashatsi mu buvuzi cyo gukora urukingo rwa COVID-19 hamwe n'imiti yemewe. Hari imiti itandukanye ya virusi iriho ivurwa COVID-19, harimo Remdesivir, Chloroquine na Hydroxychloroquine, Lupinavir/Ritonavir na Lupinavir/Ritonavir hamwe na Interferon beta iri mu bikorwa byo gusuzuma.
Kuva muri Werurwe 2020, hari ibimenyetso by'ibanze byerekana ko umuti wa Redsevere ugira ingaruka nziza.
Abarwayi bavurwaga bakoresheje umuti wa remdesivir mu buryo bw'impuhwe, bagize ihinduka mu buvuzi.
Icyiciro cya gatatu cy'igerageza mu buvuzi kirimo gukorwa muri Amerika, Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ibitero bya mbere bya Chloroquine, yari isanzwe ikoreshwa mu kuvura malaria, byatangiye mu Bushinwa muri Gashyantare 2020.
Ariko kandi, hari n'abahamagarira abandi bashakashatsi gusuzuma ubushakashatsi.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima bo muri Koreya n'u Bushinwa batanga inama yo gukoresha chlorokin.
Ariko, ikigo cyo muri Wuhan cya Virology, mu gihe gitanga inama y'uko umuntu yafata garama imwe ku munsi, kivuga ko iyo mirwi ibiri ari mibi cyane kandi ishobora kwica.
Ku ya 28 Werurwe 2020, FDA yahaye abaganga uruhushya rwo gukoresha byihutirwa hydroxychloroquine na chloroquine mu kuvura abantu banduye COVID-19. Uburyo bwo kuvura bwa 7 bwo mu Bushinwa burimo interferon, ribavirin cyangwa umifenovir mu kurwanya COVID-19.
Amakuru y'ibanze agaragaza ko dosiye nyinshi za ribavirine ari ngombwa mu kurwanya SARS-CoV-2 mu byiciro bya laboratwari.
Nyuma yo kugaragaza ko SARS-CoV-2 ifunze cyane, nitasoxanide yasabwe kongera kwiga mu mubiri. Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko guhuza poroteyine ya spike na serine intermembrane proteinase 2 (TMPRSS2) ari ngombwa kugira ngo SARS-CoV-2 yinjire binyuze mu guhura na ACE2.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bwinshi bwa chlorokin na hydroxychloroquine hamwe na azithromycin cyangwa idafite, bufite inzitizi nyinshi zituma umuryango w'abaganga utemera no kugerageza ubu buryo bwo kuvura nta bushakashatsi bw'inyongera. Slatviemir ntabwo ihagarika SARS-CoV-2 mu byumba by'ubushakashatsi kandi nta ruhare igira mu kuvura COVID-19.
Cytokine cyorezo gishobora kuba ikibazo mu byiciro bikurikiyeho bya COVID-19.
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hydroxychloroquine ishobora kugira ubushobozi bwo kurwanya ibiza bya sitokine. Tucylisomab yashyizwe mu mabwiriza y'ubuvuzi nyuma yo kurangiza ubushakashatsi bugufi bwakozwe na Komisiyo y'Igihugu y'Ubuzima y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma yo kugaragaza ibisubizo byiza ku barwayi bafite uburwayi bukabije, ubu iri mu igeragezwa ry'icyiciro cya 2 mu gihugu cyose cy'Ubutaliyani.
Ibizamini by'amaraso bifatanyije n'ibizamini bya feritini ya serum, bikoreshwa mu gupima ibiza by'ibiza by'ibinyabutabire, mu guhangana n'ibimenyetso by'ibiza nk'ibi bivugwa ko bituma abantu benshi banduye bapfa.
Igikoresho cyitwa interleukin-6 receptor antagonist cyemejwe na FDA mu 2017 ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu gihe cyahise mu kuvura indwara y'indwara ya sitokine itera indwara zidakira za siteroyi, iterwa n'impamvu zitandukanye, ni ukuvuga CAR T cell therapy.
Kugeza ubu, nta gihamya ihamye cyangwa iteganyijwe yemeza ko tucisilisumab ari umuti mwiza wa CRS.
Kwimura abasirikare barwanya COVID-19 n'abasirikare barwanya abanduye bakurwa mu mubiri w'umuntu bakize, ubu biri gusuzumwa nk'uburyo butari urukingo.
Ubu buryo bwakozwe bwageragejwe kuri SARS nta musaruro ufatika.
Kugabanya virusi ni uburyo bwitezwe bwo kuvura, aho imiti y'abanduye idakora ishobora gutuma umuntu agira ubushobozi bwo kwirinda SARS-CoV-2.
Ariko kandi, hari ubundi buryo bushobora kubaho, urugero nk'imikorere y'umubiri mu mubiri (cytotoxicity) na/cyangwa fagocytosis (phagocytosis) mu mubiri.
Hari ubundi buryo bwo kuvura budafite abasirikare b'umubiri, urugero nko gukoresha abasirikare b'umubiri b'umwanda.
Umusaruro wa seriyamu y'abantu bafite ubuzima bwiza, ikubiyemo igice cy'amaraso y'abarwayi bakize kandi irimo udukoko tw'ubwoko runaka tw'urukingo rwa virusi, ushobora kwiyongera kugira ngo ikoreshwe mu buryo bwihuse.
